5-e1ed-4bc5-addd-3e8495d5c3dc.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalandhar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Malerkotla%20district%20%E2%80%93%20which%20has%20a%20significant%20Muslim%20population%20%E2%80%93%20members%20of%20the%20community%20are%20being%20invited%20for%20Roza%20Iftar%2C%20the%20evening%20meal%20that%20is%20meant%20to%20break%20fast%20during%20Ramzan%2C%20by%20Hindu%20and%20Sikh%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20month-long%20Ramzan%20observance%20and%20fast-breaking%20festivities%20in%20Malerkotla%20are%20unique%20as%20they%20are%20not%20confined%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20There%20is%20iftar%20in%20Hindu%20temples%20and%20Gurdwaras.%20Muslims%20too%20have%20been%20inviting%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Christians%2C%20and%20members%20of%20other%20religious%20communities%20to%20join%20them%20in%20special%20Ramzan%20prayers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20erstwhile%20princely%20state%2C%20Malerkotla%20was%20founded%20by%20a%20ruler%20from%20present-day%20Afghanistan%2C%20Sheikh%20Sadruddin-i-Jahan%2C%20in%201454.%20Malerkotla%20was%20upgraded%20to%20the%2023rd%20district%20of%20Punjab%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20Captain%20Amarinder%20Singh%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20iftar%20and%20Ramzan%20prayers%20are%20being%20organised%20in%20gurdwaras%20almost%20every%20day.%20The%20president%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Brahmin%20Front%2C%20Mahant%20Swaroop%20Bihari%20Sharma%2C%20said%20they%20have%20been%20celebrating%20Roza%20Iftar%20and%20Eid%20here%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeither%20have%20we%20ever%20cared%20for%20the%20communal%20ideology%20of%20politicians%20nor%20would%20we%20let%20them%20preach%20to%20us.%20We%2C%20the%20Hindus%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20and%20Christians%20have%20been%20together%20for%20ages%20in%20Malerkotla.%20There%20are%20politicians%20who%20try%20to%20incite%20violence%20but%20no%20religion%20teaches%20hatred.%20Nobody%20wants%20to%20fight.%20I%20keep%20telling%20people%20that%20before%20they%20talk%20about%20religion%2C%20let%20us%20become%20humans%20first.%20We%20should%20celebrate%20all%20festivals%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Laxmi%20Narayan%20Mandir%20and%20Aqsa%20Mosque%20are%20situated%20adjacent%20to%20each%20other%20in%20the%20Hindu-majority%20Somsons%20Colony%20at%20Malerkotla.%20The%20temple%20and%20the%20mosque%20share%20a%20common%20wall%2C%20reflecting%20deep%20ties%20dating%20back%20to%20over%20three%20centuries%2C%20said%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20pride%20in%20Malerkotla%E2%80%99s%20rich%20culture%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Shree%20Ram%20Mandir%20Committee%20at%20Ahmedgarh%2C%20Deepak%20Sharma%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20hosting%20Roza%20Iftar%20at%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20Ahmedgarh%2C%20next%20week%20for%20which%20we%20have%20sent%20invitations%20to%20all%20our%20Muslim%20friends.%20Our%20committee%20members%20will%20also%20join%20Muslim%20brothers%20for%20Eid-ul-Fitr%20celebrations.%20Earlier%20we%20used%20to%20give%20dry%20ration%20to%20financially%20weaker%20Muslim%20families%20for%20iftar%20but%20now%20we%20are%20organising%20special%20iftar%20programmes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100827%2F254d5489-4e7b-4ba6-be42-543519c01c57-768x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100827%2F254d5489-4e7b-4ba6-be42-543519c01c57-768x1024.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100827%2F254d5489-4e7b-4ba6-be42-543519c01c57-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F