two%20children%20were%2C%20however%2C%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20the%20Sikhs%20built%20Gurdwara%20Haa%20Da%20Naara%20in%20Malerkotla%E2%80%99%20to%20honour%20the%20%E2%80%98rallying%20cry%20for%20justice%E2%80%99%20raised%20by%20Nawab%20Sher%20Mohammad%20Khan.%20It%20is%20one%20the%20most%20revered%20and%20iconic%20places%20of%20worship%20not%20only%20for%20the%20Sikhs%20but%20Muslims%2C%20Hindus%2C%20and%20other%20communities%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20believe%20that%20Malerkotla%20is%20blessed%20by%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20and%20Sher%20Mohammad%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20and%20that%20is%20why%20it%20has%20been%20untouched%20by%20communal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100838%2F6f37f370-4c9c-4603-ba7b-d7944e53b6b8-1024x576.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100838%2F6f37f370-4c9c-4603-ba7b-d7944e53b6b8-1024x576.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100838%2F6f37f370-4c9c-4603-ba7b-d7944e53b6b8-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100838%2F6f37f370-4c9c-4603-ba7b-d7944e53b6b8.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-703106%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENaseer%20Khan%20of%20Sikh%20Muslim%20Sanjhan%20Foundation%2C%20Malerkotla%20receiving%20Iftar%20gifts%20from%20a%20Sikh%20community%20member.%20Photo%3A%20By%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Adnan%20Ali%20Khan%20from%20Malerkotla%E2%80%99s%20royal%20family%20said%20that%20they%20were%20continuing%20the%20legacy%20of%20Nawab%20Sher%20Mohammad%20Khan.%20%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%20is%20Gurdwara%20Haa%20Da%20Naara%2C%20where%20Gurbani%20Kirtan%20and%20Namaz%20are%20performed%20simultaneously%20during%20Ramzan%20or%20inviting%20Muslims%20for%20iftar%2C%20Malerkotla%E2%80%99s%20history%20is%20unique.%20Even%20during%20the%20Partition%20of%201947%2C%20Malerkotla%20remained%20untouched%20by%20religious%20hatred.%20We%20feel%20proud%20that%20the%20youngsters%20are%20also%20following%20suit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20a%20prominent%20community%20leader%20Naseer%20Khan%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20communal%20harmony%20group%2C%20Sikh-Muslim%20Sanjhan%20Foundation%20in%20Malerkotla%20said%20that%20inclusive%20iftar%20invitations%20are%20not%20just%20confined%20to%20the%20urban%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20villages%2C%20iftar%20invitations%20were%20generally%20from%20the%20Sikh%20families%20including%20the%20gurdwara%20managements.%20Just%20recently%2C%20we%20went%20for%20iftar%20to%20Gurdwara%20Singh%20Sabha%2C%20Jainpur%2C%20where%20people%20from%20seven%20villages%20like%20Lohar%20Majra%2C%20Kheri%20Jattan%2C%20Amargarh%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%20were%20also%20present.%20Earlier%20we%20went%20to%20Kalain%20in%20Malerkotla%20and%20Kuthala%20villages%20in%20Sangrur%20district%20too.%20The%20list%20is%20long%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shared%20that%20sometimes%20he%20and%20members%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20get%20so%20many%20invitations%20from%20in%20and%20around%20Malerkotla%20that%20they%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20attend%20all%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseer%20proudly%20said%20that%20Hindus%20and%20Sikhs%20have%20even%20performed%20Namaz%20with%20them%2C%20a%20spectacle%20hard%20to%20find%20anywhere%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CMalerkotla%20has%20set%20a%20precedent%20in%20communal%20harmony%20in%20the%20country%20and%20we%20feel%20blessed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaseer%20lamented%20that%20such%20stories%20were%20not%20being%20covered%20by%20the%20media%20and%20that%20was%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20from%20Malerkotla%20have%20joined%20the%20ongoing%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20at%20Shambu%20border%20as%20they%20did%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20in%202020.%20They%20were%20also%20a%20presence%20when%20it%20came%20to%20relief%20efforts%20during%20the%20devastating%20Punjab%20floods%20of%202023%20and%20with%20aid%20during%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%20when%20they%20donated%20330%20quintals%20of%20wheat%20for%20the%20Golden%20Temple%20langar%20in%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Sikh%20businessman%2C%20Amar%20Singh%20Sarao%2C%20who%20runs%20the%20Guru%20Nanak%20Mission%20Sewa%20Society%20at%20Ahmedgarh%20in%20Malerkotla%20said%20that%20people%20are%20being%20fooled%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%20and%20that%20is%20why%20he%20maintains%20an%20arm%E2%80%99s%20distance%20from%20politicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Amar%20Sarao%20is%20circle%20president%20of%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD).%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20year%20we%20invite%20our%20Muslim%20brothers%20for%20iftar.%20This%20year%20too%20we%20are%20planning%20a%20good%20gathering%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711355431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F25100851%2Fdb531695-e1ed-4bc5-addd-3e8495d5c3dc.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmalerkotla-sikhs-hindus-muslims-ramzan-iftar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'In%20fact%20one%20of%20our%20temple%20priests%20Raju%20Sharma%20Pandit%20even%20organised%20iftar%20at%20his%20house%20last%20year.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmalerkotla-sikhs-hindus-muslims-ramzan-iftar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226-Time%20MP%20Spoke%20About%20'Constitution%20Change'%2C%20BJP%20Changes%20Him%20As%20Candidate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20denying%20a%20poll%20pass%20to%20a%20six-time%20MP%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20weeks%20after%20his%20remarks%20on%20the%20BJP's%20400-seat%20target%20sparked%20a%20row%2C%20the%20party%20has%20yet%20again%20sent%20a%20message%20that%20leaders%20who%20embarrass%20the%20leadership%20with%20off-the-cuff%20remarks%20stand%20to%20lose%20out%20on%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnantkumar%20Hegde%2C%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20won%20the%20Uttara%20Kannada%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20six%20times%20in%20the%20past%2028%20years%2C%20with%20four%20back-to-back%20victories.%20A%20repeat%20offender%20as%20far%20as%20controversial%20speeches%20are%20concerned%2C%20Mr%20Hegde%20raised%20a%20political%20storm%20earlier%20this%20month%20when%20he%20claimed%20that%20BJP's%20target%20to%20win%20400%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20is%20aimed%20at%20changing%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccusing%20the%20Congress%20of%20changing%20the%20Constitution%20to%20%26quot%3Boppress%20Hindus%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20told%20a%20gathering%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20%26quot%3Brewrite%26quot%3B%20the%20Constitution.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Constitution%20has%20to%20be%20amended%20--%20the%20Congress%20fundamentally%20distorted%20the%20Constitution%20by%20forcefully%20filling%20unnecessary%20things%20in%20it%2C%20especially%20by%20bringing%20in%20laws%20that%20were%20aimed%20at%20suppressing%20the%20Hindu%20society%20--%20if%20all%20of%20this%20has%20to%20be%20changed%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20with%20this%20(current)%20majority%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20MP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20think%20it%20can%20be%20done%20as%20Congress%20is%20not%20there%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modi%20has%20two-thirds%20majority%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20and%20keep%20quiet%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20the%20party%20needs%20a%20two-third%20majority%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20states%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Opposition%20slammed%20the%20BJP%20over%20its%20MP's%20remarks%2C%20the%20party%20distanced%20itself%2C%20saying%20that%20Mr%20Hegde's%20remarks%20%26quot%3Bare%20his%20personal%20views%26quot%3B.%20The%20writing%20on%20the%20wall%20was%20clear%20-%20the%20six-time%20MP%20was%20losing%20his%20seat.%20It%20is%20learnt%20that%20he%20did%20lobby%20hard%2C%20but%20the%20decision%20had%20been%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplacing%20Mr%20Hegde%20in%20the%20BJP%20stronghold%20is%20Vishweshwar%20Hegde%20Kageri%2C%20a%20six-time%20MLA%20who%20has%20also%20served%20as%20a%20Speaker%20of%20Karnataka%20Assembly%20and%20a%20state%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20selection%20of%20candidates%20this%20time%20reveals%20a%20clear%20pattern%20-%20leaders%20known%20for%20hate%20speeches%20and%20controversial%20remarks%20are%20a%20strict%20no-no.%20Before%20Mr%20Hegde%2C%20firebrand%20woman%20leader%20Pragya%20Singh%20Thakur%20and%20Delhi%20MPs%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20and%20Parvesh%20Sahib%20Singh%20Verma%20lost%20out%20on%20the%20poll%20pass%20despite%20being%20sitting%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20party%20leader%20had%20earlier%20told%20NDTV%20that%20while%20winnability%20is%20important%2C%20the%20party%20is%20also%20looking%20closely%20at%20candidates%20who%20have%20embarrassed%20the%20leadership%20by%20making%20provocative%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDenial%20of%20tickets%20to%20them%20sends%20a%20message%20that%20in%20public%20life%2C%20decorum%20has%20to%20be%20maintained.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20had%20warned%20party%20leaders%20on%20several%20occasions%20that%20they%20should%20not%20make%20controversial%20statements%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20leader%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711355220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F37tqfpq8_hegde_625x300_25_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22origin