%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2222%20Bengaluru%20Families%20Fined%20For%20Wasting%20Drinking%20Water%20Amid%20Severe%20Shortage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengaluru%20authorities%20have%20fined%2022%20families%20for%20using%20drinking%20water%20for%20non-essential%20activities.%20Each%20family%20must%20pay%20Rs%205%2C000%20fine%20for%20the%20violation%20of%20the%20water%20supply%20board's%20order%20to%20conserve%20water%20amid%20a%20severe%20shortage%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengaluru%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%20(BWSSB)%20said%20it%20has%20collected%20Rs%201.1%20lakh%20in%20fines%20from%2022%20households%20for%20using%20%26quot%3Bdrinking%20water%20for%20car-washing%20or%20gardening%26quot%3B.%20The%20fines%20were%20collected%20from%20different%20areas%20of%20the%20city%2C%20with%20the%20highest%20(Rs%2080%2C000)%20coming%20from%20the%20southern%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20BWSSB%20had%20recommended%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-penalty-for-bengaluru-residents-using-water-for-washing-cars-construction-5199048%5C%22%3Eeconomical%20use%20of%20drinking%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20keeping%20the%20crisis%20in%20mind.%20Residents%20were%20urged%20to%20avoid%20using%20drinking%20water%20for%20washing%20vehicles%2C%20construction%2C%20and%20entertainment%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20repeat%20offenders%2C%20the%20board%20had%20decided%20an%20additional%20fine%20of%20Rs%20500%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fholi-2024-know-why-the-festival-of-colours-is-celebrated-5306853%5C%22%3EHoli%3C%2Fa%3E%20celebrations%2C%20BWSSB%20has%20advised%20residents%20not%20to%20use%20Cauvery%20and%20borewell%20water%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fno-pool-party-rain-dance-bengalurus-holi-order-a