ood%2Fnews%2Fholi-2024-sara-ali-khan-stuns-in-a-saree-wishes-happy-birthday-to-this-special-person-video-inside%2Farticleshow%2F108762903.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108762903.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAdding%20to%20her%20apprehension%20is%20the%20prospect%20of%20working%20alongside%20her%20father%2C%20Saif%20Ali%20Khan.%20Sara%20reflected%20on%20their%20recent%20collaboration%20in%20an%20advertisement%20and%20expressed%20her%20desire%20to%20work%20with%20him%20on%20a%20film.%20She%20highlighted%20her%20father's%20role%20as%20a%20source%20of%20inspiration%20and%20emphasized%20the%20value%20she%20places%20on%20his%20perseverance%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20a%20trait%20she%20hopes%20to%20emulate%20in%20her%20own%20career%20journey%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fholi-2024-sara-ali-khan-stuns-in-a-saree-wishes-happy-birthday-to-this-special-person-video-inside%2Farticleshow%2F108762903.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Opinion%3A%20PM%20Modi's%20Big%20Bet%20On%20Elon%20Musk%20In%20India%20Might%20Just%20Work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk's%20long%20courtship%20of%20Indian%20officialdom%20may%20have%20finally%20paid%20off.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wanted%20him%20to%20open%20one%20of%20his%20Tesla%20%26quot%3Bgigafactories%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20efforts%20to%20expand%20its%20long-moribund%20manufacturing%20sector%3B%20Musk%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20wanted%20India%20to%20address%20tariffs%20on%20electric%20vehicle%20imports%20that%20rendered%20foreign-made%20Teslas%20uncompetitive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2015%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20a%20new%20scheme%20to%20promote%20investment%20in%20EVs.%20Any%20company%20willing%20to%20invest%20%24500%20million%20in%20a%20new%20manufacturing%20facility%20that%20begins%20production%20in%20three%20years%20(and%20with%20at%20least%20a%20quarter%20of%20its%20components%20added%20locally%2C%20to%20begin%20with)%20will%20also%20be%20allowed%20to%20import%208%2C000%20high-end%20vehicles%20a%20year%20at%20a%20lower%20tariff%20of%2015%25.%20It's%20generally%20assumed%20that%20this%20quid%20pro%20quo%20will%20be%20enough%20to%20get%20Musk%20-%20and%2C%20hopefully%2C%20one%20or%20two%20other%20companies%2C%20like%20Vietnam's%20Vinfast%20Auto%20Ltd.%20-%20to%20bite.%20Certainly%2C%20the%20EV%20producers%20that%20currently%20dominate%20the%20Indian%20market%20are%20already%20bracing%20for%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20this%20looks%20like%20business%20as%20usual.%20Officials%20have%20made%20a%20habit%20of%20using%20the%20supposed%20potential%20of%20the%20domestic%20market%20as%20an%20inducement%20for%20foreign%20investors.%20The%20stick%20of%20high%20tariffs%20together%20with%20the%20carrot%20of%20possible%20consumer%20demand%20growth%20should%20be%20enough%20to%20lure%20in%20people%20like%20Musk%2C%20they%20think.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20there's%20a%20deeper%20story%20to%20be%20told%20here.%20Size%20matters%3A%20The%20Indian%20government%20is%20a%20big%20believer%20in%20the%20transformative%20potential%20of%20a%20single%20large%20investor.%20Officials%20expended%20enormous%20amounts%20of%20energy%20wooing%20Apple%20Inc.%20They%20were%20ultimately%20successful%2C%20and%20now%20think%20an%20entire%20mobile%20phone%20manufacturing%20ecosystem%20will%20grow%20up%20around%20Foxconn%20Technology%20Co.'s%20factories%20in%20south%20India.%20For%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20they've%20been%20working%20to%20convince%20Taiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Co.%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20It's%20an%20anchor%20investor%20strategy%3A%20Get%20a%20whale%20like%20Musk%20in%2C%20and%20the%20minnows%20will%20follow.%20If%20Apple%20and%20Tesla%20are%20both%20putting%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20into%20backing%20the%20India%20story%2C%20it%20is%20something%20of%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20country's%20business%20environment%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20governments%20have%20tried%20this%2C%20of%20course.%20China%20famously%20waived%20its%20domestic%20ownership%20requirements%20to%20get%20Tesla%20to%20open%20a%20gigafactory%20in%20Shanghai.%20That%20seems%20to%20have%20paid%20off%3A%20Tesla%20says%20that%20over%2095%25%20of%20the%20parts%20that%20factory%20uses%20come%20from%20local%20suppliers.%20And%20Musk's%20claim%20that%20he%20couldn't%20invest%20big%20in%20a%20country%20that%20didn't%20allow%20him%20to%20get%20enough%20cars%20on%20the%20ground%20first%20did%20have%20a%20certain%20logic.%20Importing%20vehicles%20to%20begin%20with%20allows%20you%20to%20start%20creating%20a%20charging%20infrastructure%2C%20for%20example.%20That%20in%20turn%20grows%20the%20domestic%20market%20enough%20to%20justify%20the%20investment%20you%20make%20in%20local%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20lot%20more%20that%20India%20could%20do%20to%20help%20this%20trend%20along.%20For%20example%2C%20EV%20makers%20who%20take%20up%20this%20offer%20should%20be%20encouraged%20to%20invest%20in%20interoperable%20charging.%20Land%20is%20scarce%2C%20and%20finding%20space%20for%20multiple%20different%20kinds%20of%20EV%20charging%20stations%20would%20otherwise%20be%20a%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla%20does%20have%20an%20advantage%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20making%20deals%20like%20this%3A%20Its%20business%20model%20stresses%20vertical%20integration.%20That's%20why%20its%20factories%20are%20giga-sized%2C%20after%20all.%20It's%20easier%20for%20them%20to%20make%20promises%20about%20localization%20since%20they%20have%20greater%20control%20over%20their%20supply%20chains%20than%20their%20competitors%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20will%20local%20companies%20deal%20with%20new%20entrants%20into%20India's%20EV%20market%3F%20The%20optimistic%20take%20here%20is%20that%20companies%20like%20Tata%20Motors%20Ltd.%2C%20if%20they're%20worried%20about%20competition%20from%20the%20Teslas%20of%20the%20world%20now%20that%20tariffs%20have%20come%20down%2C%20should%20argue%20more%20strenuously%20for%20lower%20trade%20barriers%20all%20round.%20That's%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20would%20keep%20them%20competitive%2C%20given%20their%20more%20expansive%20supply%20chains.%20The%20automobile%20sector%20needs%20to%20become%20the%20loudest%20voice%20in%20favor%20of%20trade%20deals%20like%20the%20ones%20the%20country%20is%20currently%20negotiating%20with%20the%20UK%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%20Manufacturing%20will%20only%20take%20off%20when%20the%20business%20climate%20really%20improves%20-%20when%20tariffs%20are%20low%20and%20stable%2C%20and%20regulators%20are%20as%20welcoming%20to%20smaller%20companies%20as%20they%20are%20to%20whales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20big%20bet%20on%20big%20companies%20may%20pay%20off.%20This%20is%20clearly%20where%20its%20industrial%20policy%20is%20going%20now%3A%20relying%20on%20trusted%20foreign%20partners%20to%20transform%20entire%20sectors.%20But%2C%20you%20ask%2C%20can%20you%20trust%20Tesla%20with%20a%20task%20of%20this%20magnitude%3F%20Or%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20given%20his%20history%20of%20missed%20deadlines%20and%20impulsive%20business%20decisions%3F%20The%20government%20may%20have%20bet%20on%20Tesla%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20taking%20any%20chances%2C%20either.%20Any%20company%20choosing%20to%20take%20India's%20deal%20will%20also%20have%20to%20put%20up%20a%20bank%20guarantee%20in%20case%20it%20fails%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20its%20promises%20of%20investment%20and%20local%20sourcing.%20Trust%2C%20but%20verify%20bank%20details%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Mihir%20Swarup%20Sharma%20is%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711349040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F8dpn6ua_elon-musk-pm-modi-_625x300_21_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpm-modis-big-bet-on-elon-musk-in-india-might-just-work-5306530%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20wanted%20Elon%20Musk%20to%20open%20one%20of%20his%20Tesla%20%26quot%3Bgigafactories%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country%2C%20as%20part%20of%20its%20efforts%20to%20expand%20its%20long-moribund%20manufacturing%20sector%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpm-modis-big-bet-on-elon-musk-in-india-might-just-work-5306530%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Taapsee%20Pannu%20and%20Mathias%20Boe%20are%20married%20now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711348988000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108762791%2Cimgsize-52998.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftaapsee-pannu-and-mathias-boe-are-married-now-say-reports%2Farticleshow%2F108762801.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108762801.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EReports%20suggest%20Taapsee%20Pannu%20married%20Mathias%20Boe%20in%20an%20intimate%20ceremony%20in%20Udaipur%20on%20March%2023.%20The%20pre-wedding%20festivities%20began%20on%20March%2020%2C%20with%20few%20Bollywood%20figures%20in%20attendance%2C%20including%20Anurag%20Kashyap%2C%20Pavail%20Gulati%2C%20and%20Kanika%20Dhillon.%20The%20couple%20met%20in%202013%20at%20the%20Indian%20Badminton%20League.%20Taapsee%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20'Dunki.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Ftaapsee-pannu-and-mathias-boe-are-married-now-say-reports%2Farticleshow%2F108762801.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Conditions%2C%20Expectations%26quot%3B%3A%20Mining%20Baron%20Janardhana%20Reddy%20Rejoins%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Karnataka%20Minister%20and%20mining%20baron%20G%20Janardhana%20Reddy%20on%20Monday%20rejoined%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gangavati%20MLA%2C%20who%20is%20an%20accused%20in%20an%20illegal%20mining%20case%2C%20had%20formed%20the%20'Kalyana%20Rajya%20Pragati%20Paksha'%20(KRPP)%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls%20last%20year%2C%20snapping%20his%20two-decade-old%20association%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20today%20merged%20his%20KRPP%20with%20the%20BJP%20as%20he%2C%20along%20with%20wife%20Aruna%20Lakshmi%20and%20some%20family%20members%2C%20joined%20the%20party%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20its%20veteran%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20B%20S%20Yediyurappa%2C%20state%20President%20B%20Y%20Vijayendra%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20had%20recently%20met%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20February%2027%20Rajya%20Sabha%20polls%20he%20had%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20Congress%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bhome%20coming%26quot%3B%2C%20Reddy%20explained%20that%20the%20move%20to%20merge%20KRPP%20with%20the%20BJP%20is%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20Narendra%20Modi%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20a%20third%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmit%20Shah%20had%20invited%20me%20to%20Delhi%20and%20told%20me%20that%20--%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20extending%20outside%20support%20(KRPP%20supporting%20BJP%20in%20LS%20polls)%20and%20instead%20I%20should%20join%20the%20BJP%20and%20work%20for%20it%2C%20as%20I%20took%20my%20political%20birth%20in%20the%20party.%20Accepting%20it%2C%20I'm%20joining%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraising%20Yediyurappa%20and%20the%20leader's%20contribution%20in%20his%20political%20growth%2C%20Reddy%20said%20he%20is%20happy%20that%20he%20will%20be%20working%20in%20the%20party%20now%20with%20the%20veteran%20leader's%20son%20Vijayendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20work%20as%20a%20common%20party%20worker%20along%20with%20other%20leaders%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Vijayendra.%20I%20have%20not%20come%20with%20any%20conditions%20or%20expectations.%20Whatever%20responsibility%20the%20party%20gives%20me%2C%20I%20will%20honestly%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBJP%20was%20always%20there%20in%20my%20blood%2C%20but%20due%20to%20some%20reasons%20I%20had%20gone%20out%2C%20but%20today%20I%20feel%20I%20have%20come%20back%20to%20my%20mother's%20lap.%20Looking%20at%20my%20brothers%20here%2C%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20I'm%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20BJP%20office%20after%2013%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcoming%20Reddy%20back%20into%20the%20party%2C%20Vijayendra%20said%20his%20joining%20will%20strengthen%20BJP%20in%20the%20Kalyana%20Karnataka%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLiking%20Narendra%20Modi's%20leadership%20and%20accepting%20BJP's%20ideology%2C%20Reddy%20has%20rejoined%20the%20party.%20Reddy%20has%20said%20that%20Karnataka%20should%20have%20a%20larger%20contribution%20in%20making%20Modi%20PM%20once%20again%20--%20to%20ensure%20that%20BJP%20and%20JD(S)%20alliance%20win%20all%20the%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20is%20merging%20his%20KRPP%20with%20BJP%20and%20is%20joining%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20assembly%20polls%20last%20year%2C%20Reddy%20had%20been%20largely%20politically%20inactive%20for%20nearly%2012%20years%20since%20his%20arrest%20by%20the%20CBI%20for%20an%20alleged%20role%20in%20a%20mining%20scam.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20he%20had%20a%20brief%20stint%20ahead%20of%20the%202018%20assembly%20polls%20when%20he%20campaigned%20for%20his%20close%20friend%20and%20former%20Minister%20B%20Sriramulu%20in%20Molakalmuru%20Assembly%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202018%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20then%20BJP%20national%20president%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20reporter's%20question%2C%20had%20distanced%20the%20party%20from%20him%20and%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20BJP%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Janardhana%20Reddy.%26quot%3B%20Accused%20in%20a%20multi-crore%20illegal%20mining%20case%2C%20he%20has%20been%20out%20on%20bail%20since%202015.%20Several%20conditions%20were%20imposed%20by%20the%20top%20court%20in%20its%20order%20which%20includes%20prohibiting%20him%20from%20visiting%20Ballari%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Ananthpur%20and%20Kadapa%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20of%20these%20restrictions%2C%20he%20had%20to%20contest%20the%202023%20Assembly%20polls%20from%20Gangavati%20in%20Koppal%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20his%20displeasure%20about%20the%20way%20BJP%20had%20ignored%20him%2C%20Reddy%20had%20announced%20a%20new%20party%20last%20year%20and%20also%20took%20a%20dig%20at%20his%20brothers%20--%20Karunakara%20Reddy%20and%20Somashekar%20Reddy%20--%20and%20Sriramulu%2C%20as%20they%20remained%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20of%20them%20had%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20the%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20with%20Reddy's%20new%20party%20said%20to%20have%20impacted%20their%20performance%20in%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESriramulu%2C%20a%20ST%20community%20leader%20and%20former%20Minister%20is%20now%20the%20BJP's%20candidate%20from%20the%20Bellary%20(Ballari)%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20had%20played%20an%20instrumental%20role%20in%20strengthening%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Ballari%20district%20and%20is%20still%20believed%20to%20enjoy%20a%20considerable%20clout%20there%20as%20well%20as%20in%20adjoining%20districts%20like%20Chitradurga%2C%20Koppal%20and%20Raichur%2C%20which%20could%20be%20useful%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20and%20his%20brother-in-law%20B%20V%20Srinivas%20Reddy%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Obalapuram%20Mining%20Company%20(OMC)%2C%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20on%20September%205%2C%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20accused%20of%20changing%20mining%20lease%20boundary%20markings%20and%20indulging%20in%20illegal%20mining%20in%20the%20Ballari%20Reserve%20Forest%20area%2C%20spread%20over%20Ballari%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20the%20Anantpur%20district%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReddy%20first%20came%20to%20political%20limelight%20during%20the%201999%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20when%20he%20campaigned%20for%20BJP%20leader%2C%20the%20late%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20who%20had%20contested%20against%20Congress'%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20from%20Ballari.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20Minister%20T%20John's%20son%20Thomas%20John%20also%20joined%20the%20BJP%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711348980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fpe9ueobg_janardhana-reddy_625x300_24_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fno-conditions-expectations-mining-baron-janardhana-reddy-rejoins-bjp-5306469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Karnataka%20Minister%20and%20mining%20baron%20G%20Janardhana%20Reddy%20on%20Monday%20rejoined%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20