0expressed%20joy%20in%20celebrating%20with%20incredible%20people%20in%20India.%20Priyanka%20shared%20photos%20on%20Instagram%2C%20thanking%20Isha%20and%20Anand%20Piramal%20for%20the%20fun%20time.%20Nick%20recently%20performed%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20where%20he%20was%20cheered%20as%20'Jiju'%20(sister's%20husband)%20by%20the%20crowd.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-priyanka-chopra-and-nick-jonas-celebrated-holi-with-isha-ambani%2Farticleshow%2F108762681.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kate%20Middleton%20is%20undergoing%20preventative%20chemotherapy%3A%20All%20you%20need%20to%20know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711348371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108762642%2Cimgsize-1096754.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fkate-middleton-is-undergoing-preventative-chemotherapy-all-you-need-to-know%2Farticleshow%2F108762640.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108762640.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fkate-middleton-is-undergoing-preventative-chemotherapy-all-you-need-to-know%2Farticleshow%2F108762640.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fkate-middleton-is-undergoing-preventative-chemotherapy-all-you-need-to-know%2Famp_articleshow%2F108762640.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fkate-middleton-is-undergoing-preventative-chemotherapy-all-you-need-to-know%2Famp_articleshow%2F108762640.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam's%20History%20of%20Exploitation%20and%20the%20Movements%20That%20Emerged%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F12%2F19180955%2FWhatsApp-Image-2019-12-19-at-6.05.35-PM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20in%20Assam%20to%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20on%20March%2011%2C%202024%20deserves%20a%20dispassionate%20study.%20To%20know%20the%20real%20reason%20behind%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20movement%20of%201979%20to%201985%20and%20current%20discontentment%20one%20needs%20to%20trace%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20problem.%20And%20how%20the%20whole%20issue%20has%20been%20shrewdly%20deflected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20very%20outset%20it%20should%20be%20understood%20that%20Assam%20emerged%20as%20a%20sort%20of%20economic%20powerhouse%20during%20British%20India%20and%20that%20too%20without%20witnessing%20industrialisation%20%E2%80%93%20unlike%20in%20the%20case%20of%20what%20was%20then%20Bombay%20and%20Bengal.%20It%20is%20another%20thing%20that%20after%20the%20creation%20of%20East%20Pakistan%2C%20it%20lost%20Dhaka%20and%20Chittagong%20ports%20and%20became%20a%20landlocked%20state.%20Thus%20started%20the%20economic%20decline%20of%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPartition%20in%201947%20and%20the%20subsequent%20creation%20of%20Bangladesh%20in%201971%20after%20nine%20months%20of%20liberation%20struggle%20forced%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Hindu%20as%20well%20as%20Muslim%20Bengalis%20to%20settle%20in%20the%20state.%20But%20Assam%20was%20not%20the%20lone%20state%20to%20see%20such%20infiltration.%20West%20Bengal%20and%20other%20northeastern%20states%20also%20witnessed%20surge%20in%20population%20of%20people%20from%20across%20the%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20since%20the%20ground%20situation%20in%20Assam%20was%20somewhat%20different%2C%20it%20led%20to%20widespread%20discontentment%20and%20by%20late%201970s%2C%20started%20the%20movement%20against%20the%20%E2%80%98outsiders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20preparation%20of%20the%20electoral%20roll%20before%20the%201979%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20was%20the%20immediate%20cause%20for%20All%20Assam%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20and%20Assam%20Gana%20Sangram%20Parishad%20to%20launch%20a%20civil%20disobedience%20movement%20which%20at%20times%20turned%20violent%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20exploitation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20process%20of%20economic%20exploitation%20had%20actually%20started%20in%20early%2019th%20century%2C%20that%20is%20before%20the%20advent%20of%20railways%20and%20automobile.%20The%20British%20colonisers%20started%20looting%20the%20rich%20forest%20wealth%20of%20the%20northeast%20just%20years%20after%20occupying%20it%20in%20late%3Cbr%3E%5Cnthe%2018th%20century.%20As%20it%20was%20quite%20easy%20to%20directly%20transport%20timber%2C%20bamboo%2C%20cane%2C%20tea%20and%20cash%20crops%20from%20the%20deep%20interiors%20of%20Assam%20by%20ships%20through%20the%20river%20Brahmaputra%20to%20Britain%2C%20the%20region%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20introduced%20the%20cultivation%20of%20poppy%20in%20Assam%20and%20Bengal%20to%20produce%20opium%20which%20was%20smuggled%20to%20China%2C%20from%20where%20Britain%20was%20facing%20trade%20deficit.%20This%20led%20to%20two%20Opium%20Wars%20in%20the%20mid-19th%20century.%20The%20British%20grew%20rich%20by%20this%20totally%20unethical%20means%20but%20the%20poor%20people%20of%20Assam%20had%20to%20pay%20dearly.%20The%20local%20farmers%20were%20forced%20to%20produce%20cash%20crops%20which%20benefited%20the%20British%20as%20well%20as%20traders%20from%20north%20and%20west%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20state%20saw%20a%20lot%20of%20economic%20activities%2C%20it%20became%20the%20centre%20of%20exploitation%20of%20labours%2C%20both%20local%20and%20indentured%20ones%20brought%20mainly%20from%20Chotanagpur%20region%20of%20east-central%20India.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20them%20were%20Adivasis%2C%20mostly%20Santhals%2C%20forcibly%20uprooted%20from%20their%20land%20and%20sent%20to%20work%20in%20tea%20gardens%20in%20Assam.%20The%20imperialist%20power%20wanted%20to%20hit%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone.%20They%20crushed%20the%20rebellious%20Adivasis%20of%20what%20was%20then%20Bengal%2C%20now%20Jharkhand%2C%20in%2019th%20century%20and%20at%20the%20same%20time%20replaced%20the%20local%20aboriginal%20people%20of%20Assam%20who%20were%20also%20the%20victims%20of%20the%20exploitative%20land%20revenue%20policy%20of%20the%20British%20masters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-black-day-for-assam-anti-caa-protests-erupt-in-assam-again-post-mha-notification%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98A%20Black%20Day%20For%20Assam%E2%80%99%3A%20Anti-CAA%20Protests%20Erupt%20In%20Assam%20After%20MHA%20Notification%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20also%20brought%20with%20them%20educated%20Hindu%20Bengalis%20from%20Bengal%20who%20occupied%20the%20second%20and%20third%20rung%20of%20bureaucracy.%20The%20rise%20of%20business%20activities%20in%20Assam%20facilitated%20neighbouring%20Bengal%20too.%20A%20sense%20of%20alienation%20started%20gripping%20the%20people%20of%20the%20northeast%2C%20in%20particular%20Assam%2C%20even%20in%20the%20pre-Independence%20era.%20They%20eagerly%20took%20part%20in%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%20peaceful%20struggle%20for%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPost-Partition%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20after%20Partition%2C%20the%20situation%20turned%20worse%20as%20Assam%20lost%20the%20naval%20opening%20following%20the%20loss%20of%20East%20Pakistan%20ports.%20Now%20far-away%20Kolkata%20became%20the%20only%20place%20from%20where%20trade%20could%20be%20done.%20A%20road%20or%20rail%20journey%20to%20any%20place%20in%20interior%20Assam%20from%3Cbr%3E%5CnKolkata%20takes%20a%20much%20longer%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20as%20British%20rulers%20were%20keen%20to%20develop%20Kolkata%2C%20the%20then%20capital%20of%20India%2C%20they%20set%20up%20head%20offices%20of%20tea%20companies%20and%20tea%20processing%20plants%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sense%20started%20prevailing%20among%20the%20Assamese%20that%20their%20state%20has%20become%20a%20colony%20of%20not%20just%20British%20masters%20but%20also%20of%20better%20educated%20Bengalis%20and%20traders%20from%20north%20and%20west%20India.%20Assam%20gradually%20started%20losing%20attraction%20following%20developments%20in%20the%20post-1947%20years.%20When%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20movement%20was%20launched%20in%201979%20it%20was%20not%20communal%20in%20nature.%20As%20there%20was%20widespread%20resentment%20among%20the%20people%20not%20only%20against%20migrants%20from%20East%20Pakistan%20or%20later%20Bangladesh%20but%20against%20all%20those%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20India%20too%2C%20whom%20they%20dubbed%20as%20exploiters.%20In%20the%20tea%20gardens%20too%2C%20there%20was%20a%20thin%20dividing%20line%20between%20poor%20Santhals%20brought%20from%20Chotanagpur%20belt%20more%20than%20150%20years%20ago%20and%20the%20aboriginal%20tribes%20of%20Assam.%20The%20tragedy%20is%20that%20these%20Santhals%20and%20other%20Adivasis%20from%20outside%20do%20not%20enjoy%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20status%20in%20Assam.%20Only%20the%20indigenous%20tribes%20get%20this%20facility.%20The%20bloody%20Bodo-Santhal%20clashes%20are%20common%20phenomenon%20even%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAssam%20Accord%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20August%2015%2C%201985%20Assam%20Accord%20between%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20and%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20movement%20March%2024%2C%201971%20was%20fixed%20as%20the%20cut%20off%20date%20for%20detecting%20illegal%20foreigners.%20This%20date%20is%20significant%20as%20on%20March%2025%20that%20year%20the%3Cbr%3E%5CnPakistani%20army%20launched%20a%20brutal%20crackdown%20on%20the%20victorious%20Awami%20League%20supporters%20in%20the%20then%20East%20Pakistan.%20This%20sparked%20off%20a%20civil%20war%20which%20continued%20till%20December%2016%2C%201971%20when%20Pakistani%20army%20subsequently%20surrendered%20to%20Indian%20forces.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20lakhs%20of%20refugees%20from%20there%20crossed%20over%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvolatile-situation-likely-to-arise-if-caa-implemented-16-assam-opposition-parties-to-modi%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Volatile%20Situation%20Likely%20to%20Arise%20If%20CAA%20Implemented%E2%80%99%3A%2016%20Assam%20Opposition%20Parties%20to%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20short%2C%20the%20story%20of%20Assam%20is%20complicated.%20From%20the%20very%20beginning%20in%20early%201980s%20attempts%20were%20made%20by%20vested%20interest%20to%20communalise%20the%20whole%20situation.%20Those%20who%20were%20controlling%20business%20and%20other%20sectors%20of%20Assam%2C%20were%20mostly%20from%20outside%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20tried%20to%20give%20a%20new%20twist%20as%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20movement%20was%20actually%20directed%20against%20them%20too.%20The%20Sangh%20Parivar%20became%20active%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20passed%20in%20December%202019%20did%20not%20solve%20the%20real%20problem%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Assam.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20state%20exploded%20forcing%20the%20government%20to%20cancel%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-Shinzo%20Abe%20Summit%20in%20mid-December%20in%20Guwahati.%20Five%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20that%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20CAA%20is%20concerned%20in%20Assam%20the%20BJP%20is%20caught%20in%20a%20bind.%20But%20the%20saffron%20party%20may%20try%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20it%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22