.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Picks%20Kerala%20Chief%20K%20Surendran%20To%20Take%20On%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20In%20Wayanad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20will%20face%20Kerala%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Surendran%20in%20the%20high-profile%20Wayanand%20constituency%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWayanad%2C%20a%20Congress%20stronghold%2C%20has%20been%20with%20the%20party%20since%202009.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20won%20it%20in%202019%20and%20retained%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20membership%2C%20having%20lost%20his%20Amethi%20seat%20to%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20rival%20this%20time%2C%20Mr%20Surendran%2C%20has%20the%20significant%20task%20of%20challenging%20the%20Congress-Left%20binary%20in%20Kerala's%20political%20landscape.%20Both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left%20are%20in%20a%20national%20alliance%20though%20they%20remain%20rivals%20in%20this%20southern%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Surendran%20finished%20third%20in%20Pathanamthitta%20constituency%20behind%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Left.%20He%20had%20lost%20the%202016%20assembly%20polls%20from%20Manjeswaram%20by%20merely%2089%20votes.%20He%20also%20contested%20a%20bypoll%20in%202019%2C%20but%20lost%20it%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20appointed%20to%20head%20the%20BJP%20Kerala%20unit%20in%202020%20and%20became%20the%20face%20of%20the%20protests%20against%20the%20entry%20of%20young%20women%20into%20Sabarimala%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Surendran%2C%20who%20is%20from%20Kozhikode%2C%20figured%20in%20the%20BJP's%20fifth%20candidates'%20list%2C%20which%20also%20named%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%20and%20former%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWayanad%20is%20the%20second%20Kerala%20seat%20to%20see%20a%20battle%20of%20titans%20after%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20where%20Union%20Minister%