0'Khela%20Hobe'%20In%20Bengal's%20Tamluk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20most-watched%20Lok%20Sabha%20contests%20in%20Bengal%20this%20time%20is%20the%20fight%20for%20Tamluk%20seat%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20former%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20has%20chosen%20its%20young%20leader%20and%20head%20of%20its%20social%20media%20cell%20Debangshu%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gangopadhyay%2C%20who%20resigned%20as%20a%20judge%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20days%20later%2C%20made%20headlines%20in%202021%20for%20his%20strong%20observations%20and%20directions%20to%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20investigate%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20recruitment%20of%20teachers%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20School%20Service%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2061-year-old%20has%20come%20under%20criticism%20following%20his%20switch%20from%20judiciary%20to%20politics%2C%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20alleging%20political%20motives%20behind%20his%20rulings%20in%20the%20alleged%20teacher%20recruitment%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Trinamool%20march%20soon%20after%20his%20BJP%20entry%2C%20Trinamool%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20described%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BBJP%20babu%20who%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20bench%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20she%20will%20ensure%20his%20defeat%20if%20he%20contests%20the%20election.%20With%20the%20BJP%20announcing%20him%20as%20a%20candidate%20in%20its%20fifth%20list%20released%20last%20night%2C%20the%20stage%20is%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20had%20also%20said%20that%20the%20former%20judge%20has%20become%20a%20leader%20%26quot%3Bafter%20denying%20jobs%20to%20thousands%20of%20students%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BBe%20ready.%20Wherever%20you%20contest%20from%2C%20I%20will%20send%20students%20to%20fight%20you.%26quot%3B%20For%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20weeks%2C%20buzz%20over%20Mr%20Gangopadhyay%20contesting%20from%20Tamluk%20was%20doing%20the%20rounds.%20Anticipating%20this%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20fielded%2027-year-old%20Bhattacharya%20to%20take%20on%20the%20former%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhattacharya%20has%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20student%20politics%20as%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Chhatra%20Parishad%20and%20has%20been%20handling%20the%20party's%20social%20media%20presence%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20also%20credited%20with%20writing%20the%20Khela%20Hobe%20campaign%20song%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202021%20Bengal%20elections.%20The%20Trinamool%20wrote%20the%20campaign%20song%2C%20highlighting%20the%20local%20political%20flavour%20and%20the%20Bengal%20government's%20welfare%20schemes.%20With%20catchy%20music%2C%20the%20campaign%20song%20was%20an%20instant%20hit%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20several%20other%20parties%20tweaked%20and%20used%20it%20in%20their%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20Left%20bastion%2C%20the%20Tamluk%20constituency%20has%20been%20with%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20since%202009.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20twist.%20The%20seat%20was%20won%20in%202009%20and%202014%20by%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20who%20is%20now%20among%20the%20top%20state%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP.%20Mr%20Adhikari%2C%20then%20with%20the%20Trinamool%2C%20had%20vacated%20the%20seat%20after%20being%20elected%20as%20an%20MLA%20in%20the%202016%20state%20polls.%20In%20the%20by-election%20that%20followed%2C%20his%20brother%20Dibyendu%20Adhikari%20was%20elected%20MP.%20In%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20Trinamool%20fielded%20Dibyendu%20Adhikari%20again%2C%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20family's%20influence%20in%20the%20area%2C%20and%20predictably%2C%20he%20won.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20however%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP.%20His%20brother%20Divyendu%20held%20on%20to%20the%20seat%20and%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20just%20a%20week%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20while%20the%20seat%20has%20been%20with%20Trinamool%20for%2015%20years%20now%2C%20it%20is%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari's%20turf.%20And%20the%20Trinamool%20will%20have%20to%20move%20mountains%20to%20retain%20it%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711343760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fjqp3fvu8_abhijit-gangopadhyay_625x300_25_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhijit-gangopadhyay-debangshu-bhattacharya-ex-judge-up-against-young-leader-who-wrote-khela-hobe-in-bengals-tamluk-5306007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20the%20most-watched%20Lok%20Sabha%20contests%20in%20Bengal%20this%20time%20is%20the%20fight%20for%20Tamluk%20seat%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20fielded%20former%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20judge%20Abhijit%20Gangopadhyay%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20has%20chosen%20its%20young%20leader%20Debangshu%20Bhattacharya%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabhijit-gangopadhyay-debangshu-bhattacharya-ex-judge-up-against-young-leader-who-wrote-khela-hobe-in-bengals-tamluk-5306007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Box%20Office%3A%20%E2%80%98Kung%20Fu%20Panda%204%E2%80%99%20Takes%20Weak%20First%20Weekend%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711343615000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fkung-fu-panda-4.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235950806%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Kung%20Fu%20Panda%204%E2%80%99%20opened%20on%20top%20of%20the%20mainland%20China%20box%20office%20in%20its%20first%20official%20week%20of%20release.%20But%20its%20debut%20was%20soft%20and%20led%20the%20market%20to%20one%20of%20its%20quietest%20weekends%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20Universal-DreamWorks%20Animation%20picture%20earned%20%2414.7%20milli