the%20game.%20MI%20failed%20to%20capitalise%20on%20momentum%20brought%20by%20a%2077-run%20stand%20between%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20Dewald%20Brevis%20and%20registered%20a%20narrow%20loss%20to%20start%20the%20tournament.%20A%20crucial%20decision%20that%20decided%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20game%20was%20Tilak%20not%20taking%20a%20single%20against%20Rashid%20Khan%20in%20the%2017th%20over%20and%20backing%20himself%20to%20fire%20runs%20against%20the%20spinner%20instead%20of%20David.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20post%20match%20presentation%2C%20Hardik%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BObviously%20we%20backed%20ourselves%20to%20chase%20those%20runs%20but%20it%20was%20one%20of%20those%20days%20when%20we%20see%20the%20score%20quite%20less%20compared%20to%20what%20it%20could%20have%20been%20in%20five%20overs%2C%20I%20think%20we%20lost%20little%20bit%20of%20momentum%20there.%20It%20feels%20good%20to%20be%20back%20because%20this%20is%20one%20stadium%20where%20you%20can%20enjoy%20and%20feel%20the%20atmosphere%20quite%20lively%20and%20obviously%20the%20crowd%20was%20full%20and%20they%20got%20a%20good%20game%20as%20well.%20(On%20Tilak%20not%20taking%20the%20single%20vs%20Rashid)%20I%20think%20Tilak%20felt%20that%20that%20was%20a%20better%20idea%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time%2C%20I%20completely%20back%20him%2C%20not%20an%20issue%2C%2013%20games%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20MI%20opted%20to%20bowl%20first.%20Gujarat%20Titans%20was%20largely%20kept%20silent%20by%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20(3%2F14)%20and%20Gerald%20Coetzee%20(2%2F27)%20and%20struggled%20to%20score%20at%20a%20fine%20run%20rate.%20Sai%20Sudharsan%20(45%20in%2039%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%2C%20skipper%20Shubman%20Gill%20(31%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Rahul%20Tewatia%20(22%20in%2015%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20chipped%20in%20with%20useful%20knocks%20to%20take%20GT%20to%20168%2F6%20in%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChasing%20169%2C%20MI%20did%20lose%20Ishan%20Kishan%20(0)%20and%20Naman%20Dhir%20(20%20in%2010%20balls%2C%20with%20a%20four%20and%20six)%20early%2C%20reduced%20to%2030%2F2.%20However%2C%20a%2077-run%20stand%20between%20Rohit%20Sharma%20(43%20in%2029%20balls%2C%20seven%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Dewald%20Brevis%20(46%20in%2038%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20three%20sixes%20brought%20back%20MI%20into%20the%20game.%20In%20death%20overs%2C%20pacers%20Spencer%20Johnson%20(2%2F25)%2C%20Mohit%20Sharma%20(2%2F32)%20and%20Umesh%20Yadav%20(2%2F31)%20performed%20brilliantly%2C%20leaving%20MI%20six%20runs%20short.%20Hardik%20Pandya%20could%20score%20just%2011%20runs%20in%20four%20balls%20on%20MI%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESai%20Sudarshan%20got%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711336740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fomgqji0g_hardik-pandya-presentation-bcci_625x300_25_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fwhy-tilak-varma-denied-single-to-tim-david-mi-skipper-hardik-pandyas-straightforward-reply-5304434%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Indians%20batter%20Tilak%20Varma%20denied%20the%20strike%20to%20Tim%20David%20in%20the%2017th%20over%20of%20the%20run-chase%20against%20Gujarat%20Titans.%20Hardik%20Pandya%20was%20later%20asked%20about%20his%20take%20on%20the%20decision.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel%20besieges%20two%20more%20Gaza%20hospitals%2C%20demands%20evacuations%2C%20Palestinians%20say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711336253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108759854%2Cimgsize-984935.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-besieges-two-more-gaza-hospitals-demands-evacuations-pales