a%2C%20I%20carved%20another%20small%20Ram%20lalla%20murti%20(Stone)%20in%20my%20free%20time%20at%20Ayodhya.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKBO0rgXVPq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKBO0rgXVPq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Arun%20Yogiraj%20(%40yogiraj_arun)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyogiraj_arun%2Fstatus%2F1771489213122290035%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20sculptor%20also%20shared%20a%20picture%20of%20special%20tools%20he%20used%20to%20carve%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20statue.%20He%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThought%20of%20sharing%20this%20silver%20hammer%20with%20the%20golden%20chisel%20using%20which%20I%20carved%20the%20divine%20eyes%20(Netronmilana)%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%2C%20Ayodhya.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2051-inch-tall%20idol%20which%20shows%20Ram%20Lalla%20as%20a%20five-year-old%20standing%20on%20a%20lotus%20was%20created%20by%20Mr%20Yogiraj%20out%20of%20Krishna%20Shila%20(black%20schist).%20The%20rock%20was%20brought%20from%20Karnataka%20after%20it%20was%20found%20and%20excavated%20during%20a%20levelling%20exercise%20on%20an%20agricultural%20plot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20idol%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%20or%20%E2%80%98garbha%20griha'%20of%20the%20newly-built%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20temple%2C%20the%20Karnataka-based%20sculptor%20said%20he%20considers%20himself%20the%20%26quot%3Bluckiest%20person%26quot%3B%20on%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20I%20am%20the%20luckiest%20person%20on%20the%20earth%20now.%20The%20blessing%20of%20my%20ancestors%2C%20family%20members%20and%20Lord%20Ram%20has%20always%20been%20with%20me.%20Sometimes%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20am%20in%20a%20dream%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Yogiraj%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EWho%20is%20Arun%20Yogiraj%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EArun%20Yogiraj%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20