20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20were%209%2C000%20residents%20living%20there.%20In%20comparison%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMonaco%2C%20a%20city-state%20that's%20four%20times%20smaller%20than%20Forest%20City%2C%20has%2036%2C000%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECountry%20Garden%2C%20which%20has%20a%2060%25%20stake%20in%20the%20estate%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%20The%20remaining%2040%25%20is%20owned%20by%20Sultan%20Ibrahim%2C%20who%20was%20crowned%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmalaysia-king-luxury-cars-army-ties-hitler-sultan-ibrahim-iskandar-2024-1%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSultan%2520Ibrahim%2520Iskandar%2520has%2520been%2CHitler%252C%2520and%2520a%2520private%2520army.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eking%20of%20Malaysia%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20right%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20there%20were%20more%20than%2010%20buses%20that%20ferried%20tourists%20to%20Forest%20City%20on%20property%20tourism%20packages%20every%20day%2C%20Adilah%20said.%20While%20the%20development%20continues%20to%20struggle%20to%20entice%20people%20to%20live%20in%20its%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20empty%20condominiums%20and%20villas%2C%20its%20tourism%20strategy%20may%20have%20a%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22comparison%20of%20the%20beach%20in%20forest%20city%20on%20different%20times%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f2a87a6080194819ffac0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EForest%20City's%20artificial%20beach%20in%20March%202024%20and%20May%202022.%3Cp%3EMarielle%20Descalsota%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20BI%20visited%20Forest%20City%20on%20a%20weekend%20in%20March%2C%20there%20were%20several%20dozen%20people%20at%20the%20development's%20public%20attractions%2C%20including%20th