2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20Pauses%20NOC%20for%20Sale%20of%20Land%20Between%20People%20of%20Different%20Religions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23221556%2F2022_11img23_Nov_2022_PTI11_23_2022_000240B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Assam%20government%20under%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20has%20restricted%20the%20grant%20of%20no-objection%20certificates%20or%20NOCs%20for%20the%20sale%20of%20land%20between%20people%20belonging%20to%20different%20religions%20for%20three%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fassam-suspends-noc-for-sale-of-land-between-people-of-different-religions-for-three-months%2Farticle67979389.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20Revenue%20and%20Disaster%20Management%20(Registration)%20Department%20issued%20a%20notification%20on%20March%207%20through%20the%20state%20governor%2C%20saying%20that%20this%20pause%20comes%20after%20inputs%20from%20intelligence%20agencies%20which%20have%20allegedly%20pointed%20to%20the%20transfer%20of%20land%20involving%20people%20of%20different%20religions%20%E2%80%9Cby%20fraudulent%20means.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVested%20interests%20can%20thus%20create%20communal%20conflict%20with%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20ahead%2C%20the%20notification%20claims%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20however%20adds%20that%20if%20a%20district%20commissioner%20notes%20that%20a%20no-objection%20certificate%20is%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20necessary%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20lead%20to%20any%20breach%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%E2%80%9D%20then%20it%20can%20be%20issued%20with%20prior%20concurrence%20of%20the%20Assam%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Registration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20is%20signed%20by%20Gyanendra%20Dev%20Tripathi%2C%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Revenue%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%2014%20constituencies%20in%20Assam%20will%20be%20conducted%20in%20three%20phases%2C%20on%20April%2019%2C%20April%2026%2C%20and%20May%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20follows%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20third%20phase%20of%20the%20Himanta%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20Mission%20Basundhara%20under%20which%20only%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D%20people%20of%20Assam%20can%20apply%20to%20get%20land%20titles%20for%20government-owned%20lands.%20Himanta%20had%20earlier%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislamphobia-statecraft-assam-himanta-biswa-sarma%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Bengali-origin%20Muslims%20who%20are%20landless%20could%20not%20apply%20for%20land%20under%20this%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711283425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23221556%2F2022_11img23_Nov_2022_PTI11_23_2022_000240B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-pauses-noc-for-sale-of-land-between-people-of-different-religions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20cited%20inputs%20from%20intelligence%20agencies%20which%20have%20allegedly%20pointed%20to%20the%20transfer%20of%20land%20involving%20people%20of%20different%20religions%20'by%20fraudulent%20means'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-pauses-noc-for-sale-of-land-between-people-of-different-religions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nigerian%20pupils%20taken%20in%20mass%20abduction%20freed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711283302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F33AA%2Fproduction%2F_132862231_nigeria.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68649221%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gunmen%20rode%20through%20the%20school%20in%20Kuriga%20in%20north-western%20Nigeria%20seizing%20children%20as%20young%20as%20eight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A365%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68649221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68649221.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-68649221.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Questionable%3A%20What%20Kind%20of%20Government%20Do%20Indians%20Want%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24172220%2FIndiya-but-bigger.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20that%2C%20a%20fresh%20spate%20of%20renamings%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20new%20list%20of%20%E2%80%98ferocious%E2%80%99%20dog%20breeds%2C%20have%20you%20kept%20up%20with%20the%20news%20as%20of%20late%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeffGw_mZZPMetWYN8nF1xuB1eogL2KAEF3HKhRHn2fmKydvA%2Fviewform%3Fembedded%3Dtrue%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224077%5C%22%3ELoading%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711282237000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F24172220%2FIndiya-but-bigger.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fquiz%2Fquestionable-what-kind-of-government-do-indians-want%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Between%20that%2C%20a%20fresh%20spate%20of%20renamings%20and%20the%20government's%20new%20list%20of%20'ferocious'%20dog%20breeds%2C%20have%20you%20kept%20up%20with%20the%20news%20as%20of%20late%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fquiz%2Fquestionable-what-kind-of-government-do-indians-want%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Simultaneous%20Elections%20Will%20Be%20a%20Blow%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20Popular%20Sovereignty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F29135301%2FScreenshot-2024-02-29-at-1.52.52-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Ramnath%20Kovind%20committee%2C%20constituted%20on%20September%202%2C%202023%2C%20to%20operationalise%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20desire%20of%20%E2%80%98one%20nation%2C%20one%20election%E2%80%99%20(ONOE)%2C%20an%20oxymoron%20for%20simultaneous%20elections%20at%20each%20of%20the%20three%20levels%20of%20representative%20government%20in%20India%2C%20has%20fulfilled%20his%20bidding.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20has%20been%20expressing%20his%20fancy%20about%20it%20ever%20since%20he%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014.%20In%20recommending%20%E2%80%98ONOE%E2%80%99%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%2018%2C600%20page%20report%2C%20put%20together%20following%20a%20191%20day%20consultation%2C%20presented%20on%20March%2014%2C%202024%2C%20it%20has%20fulfilled%20its%20obligation.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kovind%20committee%20will%20go%20down%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20as%20a%20rare%20committee%20that%20was%20asked%20to%20find%20ways%20of%20implementing%20a%20fanciful%2C%20but%20unconstitutional%2C%20idea%20rather%20than%20examining%20an%20issue%2C%20which%20it%20obediently%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20former%20president%2C%20Kovind%20should%20have%20kept%20out%20of%20this%20contentious%20and%20unconstitutional%20issue.%20A%20President%20of%20India%2C%20particularly%20one%20who%20has%20had%20no%20independent%20political%20status%20or%20eminence%20before%20being%20airdropped%20on%20this%20prestigious%20chair%20due%20to%20personal%20loyalty%2C%20should%20at%20least%20be%20left%20with%20the%20honour%20of%20being%20a%20distinguished%20citizen%20beyond%20the%20contentious%20muddied%20politics%20of%20the%20country.%20Indeed%2C%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20and%20later%20her%20party%2C%20invented%20and%20operated%20with%20a%20loyalist%20president%2C%20but%20since%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20revered%20and%20projected%20as%20a%20millennial%20politician-statesman%2C%20he%20could%20have%20spared%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhawan%20from%20being%20his%20loyalists%E2%80%99%20domain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20result%20of%20the%20Kovind%20committee%20that%20had%20two%20ministers%20of%20the%20Modi%20cabinet%20%E2%80%93%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20and%20law%20minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20%E2%80%93%20along%20with%20other%20saffron%20loyalists%2C%20was%20a%20foregone%20conclusion%3B%20only%20modalities%20had%20to%20be%20suggested%20to%20wrap%20it%20in%20a%20shroud%20of%20a%20consultative%20exercise.%C2%A0%20It%20was%20obviously%20not%20an%20independent%2C%20but%20a%20guided%20panel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EModalities%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20committee%20begins%20with%20a%20statement%20on%20%E2%80%98restoration%E2%80%99%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20as%20if%20simultaneous%20elections%20began%20with%20a%20design%20and%20a%20statutory%20mandate.%20The%20beginning%20of%20the%20election%20process%20in%20India%20in%201951-52%20was%20%E2%80%98simultaneous%E2%80%99%20not%20by%20design.%20Since%20elections%20were%20conducted%20only%20at%20the%20two%20constitutionally%20designed%20levels%20of%20representative%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20to%20elect%20the%20first%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabhas%2C%20each%20for%20a%20term%20of%20five%20years%2C%20simultaneity%20became%20ingrained%2C%20and%20stayed%20for%20a%20decade%20and%20a%20half.%C2%A0%20Obviously%2C%20as%20long%20as%20these%20elected%20houses%20completed%20their%20designated%20full%20five-year%20term%2C%20the%20five-year%20cycle%20of%20simultaneousness%20remained.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20the%20framers%20of%20the%20constitution%20did%20not%20prescribe%20any%20compulsive%20modality%20to%20maintain%20the%20cycle%20at%20both%20the%20levels%20meant%20that%20in%20case%20of%20a%20premature%20dissolution%20of%20a%20house%20mid-term%20poll%20for%20a%20new%20house%20with%20a%20five-year%20term%20in%20the%20Westminster%20tradition%20was%20agreed%20by%20all.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Kovind%20committee%E2%80%99s%20contention%20that%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20cycle%20of%20simultaneous%20elections%2C%20which%20was%20disrupted%20after%20the%20initial%20decades%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%E2%80%99%20stresses%20a%20non-existent%20abnormality%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20process.%20Defined%20by%20Articles%2083(2)%20and%20172(1)%2C%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabhas%20are%20for%20five%20years%20%E2%80%98unless%20sooner%20dissolved%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20Obviously%2C%20the%20framers%20of%20the%20Constitution%20did%20not%20see%20any%20abnormality%20if%20a%20house%20was%20dissolved%20earlier.%C2%A0%20In%20fact%2C%20Article%2083(2)%20foresees%20a%20possibility%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20term%20extended%20for%20a%20year%20(at%20a%20time)%20and%20%E2%80%98not%20extending%20in%20any%20case%20beyond%20a%20period%20of%20six%20months%20after%20the%20Proclamation%20has%20ceased%20to%20operate.%E2%80%99%C2%A0%20Article%20172(1)%20unambiguously%20prescribes%20the%20same%20term%20for%20the%20Legislative%20Assemblies%20of%20the%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fone-nation-one-election-further-weaken-democracy%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%20Will%20Further%20Weaken%20Indian%20Democracy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20third%20tier%20of%20the%20Indian%20democracy%20was%20not%20clearly%20defined%20till%20the%2073%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Erd%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%2074%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20constitutional%20amendments%20became%20laws%20in%20April%201993.%20Article%20243E%20and%20243U%20make%20similar%20provisions%20for%20panchayats%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%20municipalities%20in%20urban%20areas.%20The%20irregularity%20of%20their%20elections%20in%20all%20the%20states%20irrespective%20of%20the%20party%20in%20power%20reflects%20how%20the%20grassroots%20institutions%20have%20been%20treated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDisruptions%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20has%20been%20described%20as%20%E2%80%98disruption%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20committee%20was%20ingrained%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20development%20since%20the%20electoral%20process%20was%20set%20in%20motion.%20Though%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Kerala%20assembly%20in%201960%2C%20by%20imposing%20Article%20356%2C%20was%20the%20first%20sign%2C%20the%20first%20major%20%E2%80%98disruption%E2%80%99%20came%20in%20the%20fourth%20general%20elections%20in%201967%20due%20to%20a%20weakened%20Congress%20and%20underdeveloped%20opposition%20system.%20In%20fact%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20party%20system%20just%20began%20reconfiguring.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWherever%20a%20stable%20alternative%20emerged%2C%20for%20example%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20the%20electoral%20process%20stabilised.%20But%20the%20unstable%20party%20alteration%20in%20the%20northern%20states%2C%20that%20gave%20birth%20to%20ephemeral%20coalitions%2C%20characterized%20by%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaaya%20ram%2C%20gaya%20ram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20(defectors)%20and%20%E2%80%98suitcase%E2%80%99%20(money)%20politics.%20State%20Legislative%20Assemblies%20were%20dissolved%20without%20completing%20their%20term.%20These%20imbalances%20later%20led%20to%20a%20fractured%20party%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELok%20Sabha%E2%80%99s%20first%20mid-term%20dissolution%20in%201971%2C%20de-coupled%20the%20two%20levels%20of%20polls.%20The%20Emergency%20in%201975%20perpetuated%20the%20disequilibrium.%20After%20that%2C%20synchronisation%20could%20not%20be%20achieved%20because%20elected%20in%201977%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20dissolved%20again%20in%201980.%20And%20before%20that%20state%20assemblies%20were%20dissolved%20and%20re-elected%20in%201978.%20On%20her%20return%20in%201980%2C%20Gandhi%20too%20dissolved%20the%20state%20assemblies%20and%20re-elected%20them%20in%201982.%20The%20disruption%20of%20any%20possibility%20of%20simultaneity%20thus%20happened%20due%20to%20dynamics%20of%20political%20processes%20and%20the%20undemocratic%20use%20of%20Article%20356%20of%20the%20Constitution%20by%20ruling%20parties%20at%20the%20centre%20till%20the%20Bommai%20judgment%20in%201994.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EConstitutionally%20De-creasing%20the%20Democratic%20Process%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recommending%20the%20artificial%20process%20of%20%E2%80%98de-creasing%E2%80%99%20the%20democratic%20and%20constitutional%20processes%2C%20the%20Kovind%20committee%20recommends%20a%20two-step%20process%20beginning%20with%20synchronisation%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20state%20Assemblies%20followed%20by%20municipalities%20and%20panchayats.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20recommendation%20that%20the%20tenure%20of%20state%20legislative%20assemblies%20should%20end%20with%20the%20subsequent%20general%20elections%20to%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%2C%20after%20the%20%E2%80%98appointed%E2%80%99%20date%2C%20has%20a%20compelled%20artificiality.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20committee%20introduces%20two%20new%20terms%20in%20the%20lexicon%20of%20parliamentary%20democracy%20%E2%80%93%20unexpired%20term%20and%20full%20term.%20The%20former%20to%20be%20used%20in%20case%20a%20house%20is%20dissolved%20earlier%20than%20five%20years%20and%20the%20latter%20if%20a%20house%20completes%20its%20full%20five-year%20term.%C2%A0%20The%20committee%20proposes%20to%20amend%20the%20constitution%20to%20make%20these%20concepts%20parts%20of%20the%20statute.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EObviously%2C%20in%20this%20new%20electoral%20scheme%2C%20an%20elected%20house%20would%20get%20a%20five-year%20or%20%E2%80%98full%20term%E2%80%99%20not%20only%20because%20it%20has%20been%20elected%20for%20that%20term%2C%20but%20only%20if%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20also%20completes%20its%20%E2%80%98full%20term%E2%80%99.%20The%20full%20term%20of%20five%20years%20thus%20will%20not%20begin%20from%20the%20day%20of%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20house%20after%20election%2C%20but%20a%20pre-determined%20date%20decided%20following%20suggested%20constitutional%20amendments.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20proposed%20transitory%20period%20till%20synchronisation%20is%20achieved.%20The%20report%20also%20talks%20of%20a%20possibility%20that%20elections%20are%20not%20held%20simultaneously%2C%20in%20such%20a%20case%20an%20order%20on%20presidential%20advice%20would%20be%20issued%20to%20hold%20a%20particular%20election%20at%20a%20later%20date.%20In%20short%2C%20the%20whole%20scheme%20proposes%20an%20unnecessary%20tampering%20with%20the%20constitution%20and%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPopular%20Sovereignty%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EElections%20operationalise%20and%20legitimise%20popular%20sovereignty%20for%20different%20levels%20of%20government.%20Obviously%2C%20simultaneity%20of%20elections%20at%20different%20tiers%20of%20government%20may%20not%20necessarily%20add%20to%20democratic%20spirit.%20A%20compulsive%20tying%20up%20of%20the%20lower%20levels%20elections%20with%20the%20higher%20tiers%20would%20have%20the%20impact%20of%20fudging%20of%20the%20issues%20that%20are%20raised%20at%20appropriate%20levels.%20The%20voters%20assert%20their%20democratic%20rights%20and%20entitlements%20by%20raising%20and%20asserting%20their%20sovereign%20will.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposed%20synchronisation%20up%20may%20be%20good%20for%20a%20particular%20regime%20%E2%80%93%20that%20would%20like%20the%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20by%20equivocating%20the%20issues%2C%20demands%20and%20requirements%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20with%20that%20of%20the%20intermediate%20and%2For%20national%20level%20%E2%80%93%20not%20for%20a%20federal%20democracy%20like%20India%20where%20the%20popular%20mandate%20would%20vary%20not%20only%20at%20each%20level%2C%20but%20also%20regionally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EAjay%20K.%20Mehra%20is%20a%20political%20scientist.%20He%20was%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%20Senior%20Fellow%2C%20Nehru%20Memorial%20Museum%20and%20Library%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%202019-21%20and%20Principal%2C%20Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Evening%20College%2C%20Delhi%20University%20(2018).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711281973000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F29135301%2FScreenshot-2024-02-29-at-1.52.52-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsimultaneous-elections-will-be-a-blow-to-indias-popular-sovereignty%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proposed%20synchronisation%20up%20may%20be%20good%20for%20a%20particular%20regime%20%E2%80%93%20that%20would%20like%20the%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20by%20equivocating%20the%20issues%2C%20demands%20and%20requirements%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20with%20that%20of%20the%20national%20level%20%E2%80%93%20not%20for%20a%20federal%20democracy%20like%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsimultaneous-elections-will-be-a-blow-to-indias-popular-sovereignty%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20mourns%20victims%20of%20concert%20hall%20attack%20as%20families%20of%20missing%20face%20anxious%20wait%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711281240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-crocus-city-concert_6499598.jpg%3F20240324124733%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussia-mourns-victims-of-deadly-concert-hall-attack-as-families-of-missing-face-anxious-wait-13101049%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20is%20holding%20a%20day%20of%20national%20mourning%20following%20Friday's%20concert%20hall%20massacre%20near%20Moscow%2C%20as%20relatives%20of%20the%20missing%20face%20an%20anxious%20wait%20to%20see%20if%20their%20loved%20ones%20survived%20the%20gun%20rampage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A406%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Frussia-mourns-victims-of-deadly-concert-hall-attack-as-families-of-missing-face-anxious-wait-13101049%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Frussia-mourns-victims-of-deadly-concert-hall-attack-as-families-of-missing-face-anxious-wait-13101049%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Frussia-mourns-victims-of-deadly-concert-hall-attack-as-families-of-missing-face-anxious-wait-13101049%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22T.M.%20Krishna%2C%20the%20'Richness'%20of%20Carnatic%20Ragas%20and%20the%20Music%20Akka-Demy%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F25150012%2FTMK.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20paati%20(paternal%20grandmother)%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20deepest%20influences%20on%20my%20upbringing.%20She%20was%20no%20different%20than%20most%20other%20paatis%20that%20I%20knew%20in%20our%20community%20%E2%80%93%20in%20caste-%20and%20religion-important%20Chennai%20in%20the%201970s%20and%201980s.%20She%20was%20deeply%20religiously%20orthodox.%20She%20was%20traditional%20in%20attire%2C%20prim%20and%20had%20properness%20of%20familial%20situations%20and%20code%20of%20conduct.%20She%20had%20been%20hardly%20educated%20in%20formal%20schooling%20and%20had%20studied%20till%20grade%20four.%20Yet%20she%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20contemporary%20in%20thinking.%20And%20that%20is%20where%20my%20learning%20started.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20warmest%20individuals%20that%20I%20have%20ever%20interacted%20with%20in%20my%20life.%20She%20was%20religious%2C%20but%20did%20not%20hold%20others%E2%80%99%20religious%20beliefs%20against%20them%20or%20impose%20her%20ideas%20on%20them.%20People%20were%20welcome%20to%20our%20home%2C%20no%20questions%20asked.%20Just%20for%20the%20record%2C%20we%20had%20family%20and%20friends%20and%20relatives%20with%20various%20beliefs%2C%20behaviours%2C%20and%20obnoxiousities%20visit%20us.%C2%A0%20She%20was%20happy%20to%20welcome%20them%20with%20piping%20hot%20filter%20coffee%20and%20a%20snack%2C%20talk%20to%20them%20and%2C%20importantly%2C%20listen%20to%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20had%20her%20personal%20favourites%20in%20Carnatic%20music.%20During%20my%20teenage%2C%20in%20an%20era%20in%20which%20film%20songs%20were%20seen%20as%20taboo%20in%20many%20a%20Brahmin%20household%2C%20I%20had%20a%20Samantha%20Fox%20poster%20and%20music%20tape%20as%20a%20foil%20to%20her%20Semmangudi%20Saar%E2%80%99s%20swaras.%20Paati%20understood%20that%20as%C2%A0%20my%20exploration%20of%20what%20was%20music.%20She%20did%20not%20brush%20it%20aside%20as%20a%20teen%20phase.%20There%20are%20many%20such%20examples%20of%20what%20she%20accepted%20as%20diversity%20in%20views.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20upheaval%20recently%20in%20the%20world%20of%20Carnatic%20music.%20Many%20have%20questioned%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Music%20Academy%20to%20award%20T.M.%20Krishna%20the%20prestigious%20Sangita%20Kalanidhi.%20Known%20for%20his%20controversial%20views%20and%20unconventional%20approach%2C%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20selection%20has%20stirred%20up%20dissent%20among%20the%20traditionally%20conservative%20Carnatic%20music%20enthusiasts.%20Renowned%20classical%20musicians%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20boycott%20the%20upcoming%20Music%20Academy%20conference%2C%20citing%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20presidency%20as%20the%20reason%2C%20raises%20several%20eyebrows.%20Their%20accusations%20of%20Krishna%20causing%20%E2%80%9Cimmense%20damage%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20Carnatic%20music%20world%20and%20disrespecting%20revered%20icons%20like%20Tyagaraja%20and%20M.S.%20Subbulakshmi%20prompt%20us%20to%20wonder%3A%20why%20were%20these%20concerns%20not%20voiced%20earlier%3F%20If%20music%20legends%20were%20been%20disrespected%2C%20those%20who%20did%20not%20stand%20up%20for%20it%20in%20time%20must%20have%20added%20to%20such%20disrespect%20by%20being%20silent%20about%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ECongratulations%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftmkrishna%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40tmkrishna%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20receiving%20the%20Sangeeta%20Kalanidhi%20honour.%20And%20thank%20you%20TMK%20for%20your%20service%20to%20music%20and%20society.%20And%20kudos%20to%20Madras%20Music%20Academy%20for%20this%20crisp%20%26amp%3B%20dignified%20rejoinder%20to%20some%20musicians%20throwing%20what%20I%20can%20only%20describe%20as%20tantrums.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOJC5JSPWqt%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOJC5JSPWqt%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Kavita%20Krishnan%20(%40kavita_krishnan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkavita_krishnan%2Fstatus%2F1771769635110563858%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECould%20there%20be%20underlying%20motives%20at%20play%2C%20such%20as%20envy%20towards%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20versatility%2C%20or%20the%20exploitation%20of%20political%20divides%3F%20Is%20this%20controversy%20merely%20a%20symptom%20of%20larger%20societal%20tensions%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Brahmin%20versus%20Dravidian%E2%80%99%20rhetoric%3F%20As%20the%20rift%20deepens%20within%20the%20Carnatic%20music%20community%2C%20one%20can%E2%80%99t%20help%20but%20question%20the%20motives%20behind%20each%20faction%E2%80%99s%20stance.%20Are%20we%20witnessing%20a%20genuine%20concern%20for%20the%20preservation%20of%20tradition%2C%20or%20is%20this%20merely%20a%20clash%20of%20egos%20and%20ideologies%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20rasika%20(or%20one%20who%20appreciates%20music)%2C%20is%20immaterial%20whether%20an%20artiste%20performs%20at%20Music%20Academy%20in%20Chennai%20or%20a%20wedding%20hall%20%E2%80%93%20except%20for%20acoustic%20advantages%20and%20probably%20the%20tiffin%20served%20at%20the%20canteen%20there.%20So%20then%2C%20where%20does%20the%20question%20about%20a%20%E2%80%98rich%E2%80%99%20music%20academy%20come%20in%20%3F%20If%20one%20does%20not%20like%20%E2%80%98rich%20clubs%2C%E2%80%99%20one%20has%20the%20choice%20not%20to%20participate%20in%20them.%20Surprisingly%2C%20not%20a%20single%20musician%20has%20ever%20missed%20a%20chance%20to%20perform%20at%20such%20rich%20sabhas%20in%20the%20past.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20polarisation%20among%20rasikas%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20where%20does%20the%20truth%20lie%20amidst%20the%20cacophony%20of%20opinions%3F%20And%20as%20political%20undertones%20begin%20to%20surface%2C%20one%20wonders%20whether%20Carnatic%20music%20is%20becoming%20yet%20another%20battleground%20for%20partisan%20interests.%20I%20hope%20not%2C%20for%20as%20a%20rasika%2C%20I%20equally%20enjoy%20every%20artistes%E2%80%99%20music%2C%20and%20the%20different%20styles%20of%20craft%20that%20they%20demonstrate.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20any%20of%20these%20artistes%20personally%2C%20and%20in%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20consumption%20economy%2C%20I%20consume%20their%20sound%20bytes%20and%20writings%20on%20various%20issues%2C%20as%20much%20as%20I%20do%20their%20music.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20by%20T.M.%20Krishna%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fculture-after-covid-artists-cannot-be-tone-deaf-in-the-face-of-the-real-world%5C%22%3ECulture%20After%20Covid%3A%20Artists%20Cannot%20Be%20Tone%20Deaf%20in%20the%20Face%20of%20the%20Real%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20must%20be%20careful%20about%20using%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Dharma%E2%80%99%20to%20controversies%20as%20this.%20When%20artistes%20start%20using%20it%2C%20it%20worries%20laypersons%20like%20me%20as%20to%20whether%20the%20phrase%20is%20being%20politicised%20or%20ideologically%20venerated.%20Are%20the%20original%20roots%20of%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20being%20bandied%20about%20as%20a%20fashionable%20hashtag%20or%20a%20badge%2C%20I%20then%20wonder.%20Let%20us%20hope%20that%20the%20richness%20of%20Carnatic%20music%20prevails%20over%20political%20agendas%20and%20personal%20vendettas%2C%20preserving%20its%20rich%20heritage%20for%20generations%20to%20come.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20new%20school%20of%20thought!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTMKrishna%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23TMKrishna%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYQEKYBT2id%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYQEKYBT2id%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Satish%20Acharya%20(%40satishacharya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsatishacharya%2Fstatus%2F1771775607539413103%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2024%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECritics%20condemn%20T.M.%20Krishna%20for%20his%20outspoken%20views%20on%20caste%2C%20the%20environment%2C%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20political%20Hindutva%2C%20and%20myriad%20other%20topics.%20Adding%20insult%20to%20injury%2C%20he%20articulates%20these%20views%20with%20eloquence%20and%20conviction.%20Detractors%20insist%20that%20he%20should%20stick%20to%20singing%20and%20refrain%20from%20delving%20into%20contentious%20issues.%20Critics%20level%20accusations%20at%20him%2C%20claiming%20that%20he%20undermines%20the%20time-honoured%20traditions%20of%20Carnatic%20music.%20However%2C%20Krishna%20counters%20by%20asserting%20that%20Carnatic%20music%20transcends%20religious%20boundaries%2C%20functioning%20as%20an%20abstract%20art%20form%20rather%20than%20a%20religious%20practice.%20While%20this%20perspective%20holds%20merit%2C%20it%20often%20goes%20overlooked%20by%20many.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsAMgYRTEn-4%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22T.M.%20Krishna%20Sings%20Gandhi's%20Favourite%20Hymn%20'Abide%20With%20Me'%20%7C%20The%20Wire%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20challenges%20the%20entrenched%20Brahminical%20dominance%20within%20Carnatic%20music.%20His%20political%20beliefs%20are%20his%20own.%20As%20a%20rasika%2C%20I%20do%20not%20care%2C%20and%20I%20may%20not%20subscribe%20to%20his%20views.%20But%20one%20must%20accept%20that%20he%20engages%20with%20individuals%20across%20the%20political%20spectrum%2C%20confronting%20right-wingers%2C%20centrists%2C%20and%20leftists%20alike.%20Even%20detractors%20begrudgingly%20acknowledge%20his%20brilliance%20on%20stage%2C%20where%20his%20impassioned%20performances%20have%20the%20power%20to%20move%20audiences%20to%20tears%20and%20joy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20criticism%20on%20him%20suggests%20that%20he%20lacks%20%3Cem%3Ebhakti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(devotion)%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20must%20be%20condemned.%20However%2C%20this%20argument%20overlooks%20the%20essence%20of%20his%20performances.%20Whether%20or%20not%20he%20sings%20with%20true%20devotion%20is%20inconsequential%3B%20what%20truly%20matters%20is%20the%20depth%20of%20emotion%20he%20infuses%20into%20his%20singing.%20He%20sings%20with%20immense%20%3Cem%3Ebhaava%3C%2Fem%3E%20(feeling).%20Just%20having%20a%20mark%20of%20religion%20on%20one%E2%80%99s%20forehead%20does%20not%20define%20their%20human%20values%20or%20divinity.%20Nor%20does%20the%20need%20to%20flaunt%20one%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ekalacharam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(culture)%20by%20wearing%20designer-selected%20%E2%80%98traditional%E2%80%99%20garments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20then%2C%20most%20modern%20day%20purist%20Carnatic%20artistes%20also%20use%20marketing%20as%20mainstay%20to%20remain%20commercially%20relevant%2C%20despite%20their%20god-gifted%20talents.%20Did%20our%20ancient%20forefathers%20ever%20permit%20such%20sacrilege%20%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20upcoming%20Tamil%20music%20director%20in%20the%2070s%20was%20decried%20as%20sacrilegious%20as%20he%20had%20set%20Carnatic%20ragas%20to%20popular%20film%20melodies.%20Especially%20for%20the%20purists%2C%20he%20was%20seen%20as%20non-Brahmin%20and%20outside%20of%20the%20world%20of%20those%20who%20are%20allowed%20to%20use%20Carnatic%20ragas.%20But%20then%20the%20same%20genius%20musician%20is%20now%20sought%20after%20for%20collaborations%2C%20especially%20as%20he%20has%20done%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20popularising%20such%20music.%20To%20add%2C%20it%20is%20commercially%20viable%20to%20use%20his%20association.%20Where%20are%20the%20purists%20who%20damned%20him%20at%20first%20%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20stage%2C%20TM%20Krishna%20is%20an%20innovator%2C%20fearlessly%20challenging%20established%20norms%20while%20maintaining%20the%20integrity%20of%20musical%20tradition.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20reimagining%20seating%20arrangements%2C%20allowing%20accompanists%20to%20take%20the%20lead%2C%20or%20experimenting%20with%20ragas%2C%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20bold%20approach%20reflects%20a%20deliberate%20departure%20from%20convention.%20Just%20as%20few%20artists%20had%20recently%20sought%20to%20demystify%20Carnatic%20ragas%20in%20collaboration%20with%20a%20renowned%20music%20director%3B%20Krishna%20had%20embarked%20on%20a%20similar%20demystifying%20journey%20over%20a%20decade%20ago.%20If%20artistic%20license%20allows%20for%20creative%20exploration%2C%20then%20it%20extends%20to%20the%20entire%20cohort%20of%20musicians.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20by%20T.M.%20Krishna%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcarnatic-music-plagiarism-tradition%5C%22%3EThose%20Who%20Talk%20of%20Plagiarism%20in%20Carnatic%20Music%20Know%20Not%20About%20the%20Tradition%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOffstage%2C%20Krishna%20is%20recognised%20for%20his%20progressive%20ideals%20and%20efforts%20to%20leverage%20music%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20social%20change%2C%20a%20commitment%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rmaward.asia%2Fawardee%2Fthodur-madabusi-krishna-2%5C%22%3Eearned%20him%20the%20prestigious%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20award%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20inclusion%20as%20the%20Sangita%20Kalanidhi%20awardee%20may%20seem%20paradoxical%2C%20considering%20his%20criticisms%20of%20certain%20aspects%20of%20Carnatic%20music%20upheld%20by%20the%20very%20same%C2%A0%20institution%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Music%20Academy%20%E2%80%93%20that%20has%20awarded%20him.%20Despite%20ideological%20differences%2C%20the%20Music%20Academy%20has%20chosen%20to%20honour%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20contributions%20as%20a%20musician%2C%20demonstrating%20its%20commitment%20to%20the%20craft.%20But%20if%20the%20larger%20narrative%20influences%20it%20to%20change%20its%20mind%2C%20it%20would%20have%20lost%20all%20its%20moral%20standing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Krishna%20abstained%20from%20mainstream%20commercial%20music%20festivals%2C%20including%20the%20annual%20event%20at%20the%20Music%20Academy%2C%20for%20several%20years%20speaks%20volumes%20about%20his%20commitment%20to%20his%20principles.%20He%20utilised%20this%20time%20to%20experiment%20with%20various%20aspects%20of%20music%2C%20including%20audience%20engagement%2C%20performance%20formats%2C%20and%20settings.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20decade%20and%20a%20half%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20charted%20a%20course%20that%20diverges%20significantly%20from%20that%20of%20most%20Carnatic%20musicians.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20the%20music%3B%20there%20are%20broader%20considerations%20at%20play%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Krishna%20had%20remarked.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20actions%20reflect%20his%20longstanding%20advocacy%20for%20a%20departure%20from%20the%20traditionalist%20mindset%20that%20has%20historically%20dominated%20the%20Carnatic%20music%20scene.%20Many%20Carnatic%20artists%20have%20wielded%20their%20influence%20to%20maintain%20control%20over%20aspects%20like%20language%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20tradition%2C%20effectively%20establishing%20a%20personal%20fiefdom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seems%20Chennai%2C%20colloquially%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20much%20of%20the%20conservative%20community%2C%20has%20not%20changed%20one%20bit.%20It%20loves%20its%20carpets%20and%20elephants.%20I%20am%20being%20sarcastic%20here.%20Does%20it%20live%20to%20brush%20what%E2%80%99s%20uncomfortable%20to%20discuss%20under%20a%20carpet%20%3F%20And%20it%20does%20not%20want%20to%20recognise%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room%3F%20For%20example%2C%20years%20ago%2C%20rasikas%20knew%20of%20a%20brilliant%20and%20popular%20Carnatic%20musician%20who%20loved%20his%20tipple%20too%20much%2C%20and%20rumours%20abounded%20of%20his%20drinking%20before%20concerts.%20There%20have%20been%20rumours%20of%20misdemeanour%20by%20certain%20artistes%20in%20their%20conduct%20with%20women.%20Yet%20they%20have%20been%20awarded%20and%20felicitated%2C%20without%20a%20single%20question%20about%20their%20character%20or%20social%20behaviour%20%3F%20Where%20were%20the%20questions%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emurai%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(tradition)%20then%20%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20by%20T.M.%20Krishna%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkalakshetra-sexual-harassment-empower-survivors%5C%22%3EKalakshetra%20Protests%3A%20We%20Must%20Empower%20Survivors%20to%20Speak%20Up%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20must%20start%20by%20questioning%20within%20the%20communities%20you%20belong%20to.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20simply%20walk%20away%20when%20you%20have%20the%20power%20to%20enact%20change.%20There%E2%80%99s%20a%20responsibility%20towards%20the%20art%20form%20you%20practice.%20You%20must%20critically%20examine%20its%20aesthetics%2C%20social%20dynamics%2C%20and%20culture%2C%20and%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20challenge%20the%20status%20quo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20world%20of%20Carnatic%20music%20can%20no%20longer%20hide%20behind%20the%20closed%20doors%20of%20intellectualised%20drawing%20rooms%2C%20steeped%20in%20traditional%20(or%20rather%20conservative)%20views.%20Not%20all%20traditional%20views%20are%20wrong%2C%20and%20not%20all%20modern%20views%20are%20blas%C3%A9.%20Yet%2C%20this%20is%20where%20many%20artistes%20find%20discomfort.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20rings%20true%3A%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20a%20Brahmin%20by%20birth.%20I%20know%20many%20Brahmins%20who%20consume%20meat%2C%20including%20beef.%20So%2C%20what%20nonsense%20is%20this%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20That%20is%20an%20uncomfortable%20truth%20we%20are%20scared%20of%2C%20and%20quite%20often%20use%20a%20louder%20rhetoric%20to%20brush%20the%20initial%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhat-is-sanatana-dharma%5C%22%3EWhat%20Is%20Sanatana%20Dharma%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKrishna%E2%80%99s%20unconventional%20perspectives%20unsettle%20the%20entrenched%20conservatism%20within%20the%20Carnatic%20music%20community.%20Rather%20than%20addressing%20these%20issues%2C%20we%20often%20dismiss%20dissenting%20voices%20and%20exclude%20those%20who%20do%20not%20conform.%20The%20trouble%20is%20that%20we%20expect%20our%20artistes%20to%20stick%20to%20performing%20their%20art%2C%20and%20not%20have%20a%20voice%20or%20a%20view%20around%20other%20societal%20aspects.%20We%20dislike%20being%20confronted%20about%20our%20double%20standards%2C%20where%20our%20actions%20contradict%20our%20professed%20beliefs.%20For%20instance%2C%20many%20acquaintances%20have%20their%20morning%20prayer%20rituals%20with%20as%20much%20fervour%20as%20they%20indulge%20in%20evening%20club%20activities%20including%20preference%20for%20specific%20brands%20of%20single%20malt.%20Without%20judgment%20or%20preaching%2C%20we%20rationalise%20this%20behaviour%20as%20akin%20to%20being%20a%20Roman%20in%20Rome.%20That%20is%20hypocritical%2C%20just%20to%20define%20the%20word%20for%20the%20few%20who%20have%20used%20it%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETrue%20tolerance%20and%20respect%2C%20as%20my%20paati%20taught%20me%2C%20lie%20in%20acknowledging%20that%20one%E2%80%99s%20beliefs%20do%20not%20inherently%20make%20one%20superior%20to%20others.%20This%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20is%20the%20essence%20of%20our%20Dharma.%20Music%20and%20creativity%20allow%20artistes%20leeway%20to%20have%20their%20own%20form%2C%20format%20and%20finesse.%20May%20the%20audience%20be%20the%20judge%20of%20what%20they%20like%20and%20what%20they%20do%20not.%20Similarly%20in%20a%20rich%20democracy%20that%20we%20are%2C%20I%20may%20not%20agree%20with%20the%20views%20of%20T.M.%20Krishna%2C%20but%20would%20happily%20hear%20them.%20I%20have%20a%20choice%20not%20to%20hear%20his%20art%20if%20I%20do%20not%20like%20it.%20But%20I%20would%20support%20him%20to%20allow%20him%20to%20voice%20his%20opinion%2C%20within%20the%20space%20of%20what%20our%20democracy%20norms%20permit%20%E2%80%93%20not%20what%20the%20society%20pretends%20to%20allow%2C%20for%20its%20own%20personal%20or%20ideological%20favourites.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EDr.%20Srinath%20Sridharan%20is%20a%20p%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eolicy%20researcher%20and%20corporate%20advisor.%20He%20is%20co-author%20of%20the%20public%20governance%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3ETime%20for%20Bharat%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20posts%20on%20X%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%40ssmumbai.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711280667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F25150012%2FTMK.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcarnatic-music-academy-tm-krishna%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world%20of%20Carnatic%20music%20can%20no%20longer%20hide%20behind%20the%20closed%20doors%20of%20intellectualised%20drawing%20rooms%2C%20steeped%20in%20traditional%20(or%20rather%20conservative)%20views.%20The%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20award%20to%20T.M.%20Krishna%20shows%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A80%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcarnatic-music-academy-tm-krishna%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22M%26amp%3BA%20deals%20move%20into%20slow%20lane%2C%20drop%2043%25%20in%20terms%20of%20d