lims%20could%20claim%20to%20be%20indigenous%20if%20they%20encroached%20on%20%E2%80%98satras%E2%80%99%20(Vaishnavite%20monasteries)%20land%2C%20Sarma%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20want%20to%20become%20indigenous%2C%20they%20cannot%20marry%20off%20their%20minor%20daughters.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20sending%20your%20children%20to%20%3Cem%3Emadrassas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20educate%20them%20to%20become%20doctors%20and%20engineers%20if%20you%20want%20to%20be%20called%20indigenous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarma%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20they%20should%20also%20start%20sending%20their%20daughters%20to%20schools%20and%20give%20them%20the%20right%20over%20their%20fathers%E2%80%99%20properties%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fguwahati%2Fassam-cm-himanta-biswa-sarma-lays-down-indigenous-rules-for-bdesh-origin-muslims%2Farticleshow%2F108739246.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20the%20differences%20between%20them%20and%20the%20indigenous%20people%20of%20the%20state.%20If%20they%20can%20give%20up%20these%20practices%20and%20imbibe%20the%20culture%20of%20Assamese%20people%2C%20at%20some%20point%20of%20time%20they%20too%20can%20become%20indigenous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarma%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAssam%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20population%2C%20second%20largest%20in%20the%20country%20after%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20comes%20from%20two%20ethnicities%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0Bengali-speaking%20and%20Bangladesh-origin%20migrant%20Muslims%20and%20Assamese-speaking%20indigenous%20Muslims.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%202011%20census%2C%20Muslims%20account%20for%20over%2034%25%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20total%20population%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20(63%25)%20being%20Bengali-speaking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202022%2C%20around%2040%20lak