ls%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jain%20informs%20that%20after%202008%2C%20the%20forest%20cover%20reduced%20from%20400%20trees%20per%20hectare%20to%2040%20trees%20per%20hectare.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-4-1710829067-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345150%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJain%20informs%20that%20after%202008%2C%20the%20forest%20cover%20reduced%20from%20400%20trees%20per%20hectare%20to%2040%20trees%20per%20hectare.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20irresponsible%20behaviour%20was%20not%20new%2C%20he%20adds.%20Jain%20points%20out%20that%20during%20the%20British%20Raj%20and%20the%20Zamindari%20period%20after%20Independence%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246877%2Fsaving-tiger-india-reserve-chhattisgarh-jharkhand-wildlife-trust-of-india-udanti-sitanadi-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUdanti-Sitanadi%20tiger%20reserve%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewas%20used%20as%20a%20game%20reserve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20then%2C%20anyone%20could%20shoot%20animals%20after%20paying%20a%20small%20fee.%20For%20instance%2C%20you%20could%20shoot%20a%20tiger%20paying%20Rs%2025%2C%20and%20wild%20buffalo%2C%20which%20is%20the%20state%20animal%2C%20with%20Rs%20100.%20This%20continued%20till%201972%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20we%20have%20such%20low%20numbers%20of%20tigers.%20Currently%2C%20we%20have%20just%20one%20tiger.%20This%20makes%20our%20tiger%20reserve%20different%20from%20the%20Kanha%2C%20Ranthambore%2C%20or%20Pilibhit%20tiger%20reserves.%20Because%20of%20the%20encroachment%2C%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20progress%20eco-tourism%20in%20the%20region.%20Just%20a%20year%20back%2C%20we%20did%20not%20even%20have%20any%20gypsy%20safaris%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20evicting%20encroachers%20to%20welcoming%20wildlife%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20field%20visits%20to%20the%20forest%2C%20Jain%20would%20often%20see%20large%20charred%20spots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20out%20that%20giant%20100-year-old%20trees%20were%20burnt%20down%20to%20make%20huts%20and%20farmland.%20Immediately%2C%20I%20procured%20ISRO%20images%20from%202008%2C%202010%2C%20and%202012%2C%20and%20then%2C%20I%20conducted%20surveys%20using%20drones%20to%20assess%20the%20encroachment.%20After%20comparing%20both%20the%20images%2C%20we%20found%20out%20that%20the%20reserve%20was%20a%20dense%20forest%20until%202008.%20Now%2C%20it%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20an%20open%20forest%20land%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202006%2C%20the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20was%20enacted%20and%20it%20stated%20that%20any%20member%20or%20community%20that%20primarily%20resided%20in%20forest%20land%20for%20bona%20fide%20livelihood%20needs%20before%2013%20December%2C%202005%2C%20would%20be%20entitled%20to%20forest%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20the%20ISRO%20images%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20these%20people%20settled%20here%20after%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jain%20shares%20200%20encroachers%20were%20evicted%20and%20at%20least%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land%20was%20recovered%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJain%20shares%20200%20encroachers%20were%20evicted%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20Jain%20informs%20that%20the%20forest%20cover%20reduced%20from%20400%20trees%20per%20hectare%20to%2040%20trees%20per%20hectare.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20necessary%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20encroachments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20dwellers%20seeking%20their%20documents%20in%20support%20of%20possessing%20the%20forest%20land.%20But%20when%20they%20did%20not%20cooperate%2C%20the%20officials%20asked%20them%20to%20vacate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20carrying%20eviction%20drives%20in%20this%20particular%20area%20was%20a%20big%20challenge%20for%20us.%20Our%20teams%20were%20attacked%20twice%20leading%20to%20injuries.%20My%20car%20was%20burnt%20down.%20It%20was%20heartbreaking%20for%20me%20to%20see%20my%20own%20people%20being%20beaten%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20manage%20this%20situation%2C%20I%20announced%20on%20a%20loudspeaker%20that%20since%20they%20injured%20forest%20officials%2C%20the%20police%20would%20book%20the%20masses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20gathered%20mob%20had%20asked%20the%20women%20and%20the%20children%20of%20their%20community%20to%20stand%20before%20us.%20To%20avoid%20any%20hassles%20or%20misplaced%20blame%2C%20we%20had%20a%20force%20of%20female%20forest%20rangers%20on%20the%20sidelines%20too.%20There%20were%20even%20attempts%20to%20give%20this%20whole%20incident%20a%20communal%20angle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20dwellers%20went%20on%20to%20file%20petitions%20at%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20the%20State%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20and%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20High%20Court%20against%20the%20Forest%20Department.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20judgement%20was%20passed%20in%20our%20favour%20as%20we%20had%20all%20the%20evidence%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%20dated%2020%20June%2C%202023%2C%20the%20high%20court%20disposed%20of%20the%20writ%20petition%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cencroachers%E2%80%9D%20and%20mentioned%20that%20the%20respondents%20are%20%E2%80%9Cfree%20to%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20rules%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20the%20help%20of%20forest%20guards%2C%20Jain%20was%20able%20to%20recover%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345152%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20forest%20guards%2C%20Jain%20was%20able%20to%20recover%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20order%20dated%2012%20December%2C%202023%2C%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Department%20mentioned%20that%20with%20ISRO%20images%2C%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20the%20forest%20land%20was%20encroached%20after%202005%20and%20the%20documentation%20of%20petitioners%20does%20not%20support%20their%20claims%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20informs%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176709%2Fifs-civil-servant-hero-sikkim-nrega-sandeep-tambe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20official%20%3C%2Fa%3Econducted%20the%20first%20eviction%20proceeding%20in%20January%202023.%20And%20so%20far%2C%20at%20least%20600%20acres%20of%20forest%20land%20have%20been%20restored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20also%20helped%20us%20build%20trust%20among%20other%20local%20villagers%20who%20have%20now%20become%20our%20sources%20for%20sharing%20information%20on%20poaching-related%20incidences.%20Within%20nine%20months%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20conduct%2032%20operations%20where%20we%20arrested%20134%20poachers%20and%20smugglers.%20With%20reduced%20poaching%20and%20encroachment%20cases%2C%20we%20believe%20tigers%20from%20neighbouring%20states%20will%20find%20safe%20shelter%20and%20repopulate%20the%20reserve%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPersonally%2C%20this%20work%20has%20also%20brought%20immense%20contentment%20to%20Jain.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20becoming%20an%20IFS%20officer%2C%20I%20wished%20to%20join%20the%20Delhi%20police%20force%20but%20I%20missed%20it%20by%20seven%20marks.%20This%20project%20made%20me%20do%20similar%20investigation%20work%20%E2%80%94%20from%20using%20the%20cyber%20cell%20to%20tracking%20call%20records%20and%20encroaching%20activities.%20I%20do%20not%20regret%20my%20decision%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20an%20official%20uniform%20has%20been%20given%20to%20only%20three%20units%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Army%2C%20the%20police%2C%20and%20the%20forest%20officials.%20The%20purpose%20of%20this%20uniform%20is%20to%20provide%20protection.%20It%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20protect%20our%20natural%20heritage.%20Anyone%20can%20plant%20trees.%20But%20as%20a%20forest%20official%2C%20if%20we%20cannot%20save%20a%20tree%2C%20then%20what%20is%20the%20point%20of%20new%20afforestation%20drives%3F%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20IFS%20Varun%20Jain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fvillagers-attack-forest-personnel-clearing-encroachments-in-chhattisgarh-tiger-reserve-three-hurt%2Fcid%2F1941725%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVillagers%20attack%20forest%20personnel%20clearing%20encroachments%20in%2