ates%2C%20Russia%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Serbia%2C%20and%20Poland.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20innovative%20methods%20that%20helped%20her%20cultivate%20berries%20in%20the%20harsh%20weather%20conditions%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EQuit%20law%20to%20become%20a%20farmer%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Keya%20was%20a%20lawyer%20by%20profession.%20After%20pursuing%20law%20from%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Government%20Law%20College%2C%20she%20continued%20her%20practice%20with%20law%20firms%20for%20nearly%20four%20years%20until%20she%20understood%20her%20calling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20become%20a%20farmer.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20pursuing%20law%20was%20always%20to%20later%20focus%20on%20entrepreneurship.%20But%20before%20that%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20get%20good%20access%20to%20the%20legal%20framework%20to%20build%20a%20successful%20business.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20in%20an%20impactful%20sector%20to%20create%20a%20very%20purpose-driven%20entrepreneurship%20programme%20which%20would%20not%20only%20benefit%20me%20personally%20but%20would%20also%20benefit%20the%20society%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2032-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20she%20took%20a%20break%20from%20work%20to%20understand%20the%20nitty-gritties%20of%20farming%20as%20she%20did%20not%20have%20any%20agricultural%20background.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20Keya%20started%20growing%20about%2030%20varieties%20of%20microgreens%20in%20a%20vertical%20set-up%20made%20on%20the%20terrace.%20Soon%2C%20she%20started%20supplying%20them%20to%20restaurants%2C%20and%20within%20six%20months%2C%20she%20on-boarded%2050%20clients.%20This%20boosted%20her%20confidence%20and%20allowed%20her%20to%20establish%20retail%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20t