m%2F141684%2Fkamal-shahs-medical-problem-inspired-him-entrepreneur-nephroplus-dialysis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epatients%20in%20need%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20Government%20initiated%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20National%20Dialysis%20Program%20(PMNDP)%20in%202016%2C%20operating%20under%20a%20Public-Private%20Partnership%20(PPP)%20model%20to%20offer%20free%20dialysis%20services%20to%20economically%20disadvantaged%20individuals.%20This%20programme%20encompasses%20both%20hemodialysis%20and%20peritoneal%20dialysis%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%20collaborate%20with%20the%20Government%20to%20ensure%20free%20dialysis%20care%20in%20areas%20where%20this%20essential%20healthcare%20service%20isn%E2%80%99t%20available.%20Each%20centre%20is%20staffed%20with%20a%20medical%20officer%2C%20a%20technician%2C%20a%20nurse%2C%20and%20a%20housekeeping%20staff%2C%20and%20is%20equipped%20with%20three%20dialysis%20machines.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20nephrologist%20is%20assigned%20to%20each%20centre%2C%20who%20makes%20monthly%20visits%20and%20is%20available%20for%20consultations%20and%20emergencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20renal%20care%20centres%20run%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Government%20and%20are%20located%20within%20the%20Government%20district%20and%20zonal%20hospitals.%20While%20the%20space%20is%20provided%20by%20the%20Government%2C%20THF%20provides%20the%20necessary%20staffing%2C%20machines%2C%20medicines%2C%20and%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20centres%20run%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Government%2C%20THF%20also%20operates%20a%20few%20private%20and%20independent%20Renal%20Care%20Centres%2C%20which%20provide%20cost-effective%20and%20subsidised%20dialysis%20care%20to%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20over%2064%2C000%20dialysis%20sessions%20have%20been%20conducted%20across%20the%2030%20centres%2C%20with%2028%20of%20them%20operating%20in%20partnership%20with%20different%20State%20Governments%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Meghalaya%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20remaining%20two%20are%20privately%20managed%20by%20the%20foundation.%20The%20private%20centres%2C%20present%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Punjab%2C%20offer%20dialysis%20at%20subsidised%20rates.%20The%20foundation%20is%20also%20soon%20planning%20to%20expand%20to%20even%20more%20centres%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20State%20Governments%20of%20Jharkhand%20and%20Punjab%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chandrakala%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%2C%20who%20availed%20the%20benefit%20of%20The%20Hans%20Renal%20Centre%20in%20Karnaprayag.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FUntitled-design-3-1710411629-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344876%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChandrakala%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%2C%20who%20availed%20the%20benefit%20of%20The%20Hans%20Renal%20Centre%20in%20Karnaprayag.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20patients%20like%20Chandrakala%2C%20this%20is%20a%20boon%2C%20as%20it%20saves%20them%20time%2C%20